INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (1, 'The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild', 'Explore the vast kingdom of Hyrule in this epic adventure', 'Step into a world of discovery, exploration, and adventure in The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild. Travel across vast fields, through forests, and to mountain peaks as you discover what has become of the kingdom of Hyrule in this stunning Open-Air Adventure. Now on Nintendo Switch, your journey is freer and more open than ever. Take your system anywhere, and adventure as Link any way you like. Explore the wilds of Hyrule any way you like - Climb up towers and mountain peaks in search of new destinations, then set your own path to get there and plunge into the wilderness. Along the way, you will battle towering enemies, hunt wild beasts and gather ingredients for the food and elixirs you will need to sustain you on your journey. More than 100 Shrines of Trials to discover and explore - Shrines dot the landscape, waiting to be discovered in any order you want. Search for them in various ways, and solve a variety of puzzles inside. Work your way through the traps and devices inside to earn special items and other rewards that will help you on your adventure.', 59.99, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/TVAAAOSw1Sti-6id/s-l1600.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2017-03-03', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (2, 'God of War', 'Join Kratos and Atreus on a journey through Norse mythology', 'His vengeance against the Gods of Olympus years behind him, Kratos now lives as a man in the realm of Norse Gods and monsters. It is in this harsh, unforgiving world that he must fight to survive and teach his son to do the same. Kratos is a father again. As mentor and protector to Atreus, a son determined to earn his respect, he is forced to deal with and control the rage that has long defined him while out in a very dangerous world with his son. Journey to a dark, elemental world of fearsome creatures - From the marble and columns of ornate Olympus to the gritty forests, mountains, and caves of Pre-Viking Norse lore, this is a distinctly new realm with its own pantheon of creatures, monsters, and gods. With an over the shoulder free camera that brings the player closer to the action than ever before, fights in God of War mirror the pantheon of Norse creatures Kratos will face: grand, gritty, and grueling. A new main weapon and new abilities retain the defining spirit of God of War while presenting a vision of violent conflict that forges new ground in the genre.', 49.99, 'https://www.yourdecoration.it/cdn/shop/files/Poster-God-Of-War-Key-Art-91-5x61cm-Abystyle-GBYDCO513.jpg?v=1757428995', 'Sony', '2018-04-20', 15);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (3, 'Elden Ring', 'A fantasy action RPG with a vast open world', 'THE NEW FANTASY ACTION RPG. Rise, Tarnished, and be guided by grace to brandish the power of the Elden Ring and become an Elden Lord in the Lands Between. A Vast World Full of Excitement - A vast world where open fields with a variety of situations and huge dungeons with complex and three-dimensional designs are seamlessly connected. As you explore, the joy of discovering unknown and overwhelming threats await you, leading to a high sense of accomplishment. Create your Own Character - In addition to customizing the appearance of your character, you can freely combine the weapons, armor, and magic that you equip. You can develop your character according to your play style, such as increasing your muscle strength to become a strong warrior, or mastering magic. An Epic Drama Born from a Myth - A multilayered story told in fragments. An epic drama in which the various thoughts of the characters intersect in the Lands Between. Unique Online Play that Loosely Connects You to Others - In addition to multiplayer, where you can directly connect with other players and travel together, the game supports a unique asynchronous online element that allows you to feel the presence of others.', 59.99, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/8QAAAOSwJbNiQTPS/s-l1200.jpg', 'FromSoftware', '2022-02-25', 20);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (4, 'Civilization VI', 'Build an empire to stand the test of time', 'Originally created by legendary game designer Sid Meier, Civilization is a turn-based strategy game in which you attempt to build an empire to stand the test of time. Become Ruler of the World by establishing and leading a civilization from the Stone Age to the Information Age. Wage war, conduct diplomacy, advance your culture, and go head-to-head with historys greatest leaders as you attempt to build the greatest civilization the world has ever known. Civilization VI offers new ways to engage with your world: cities now physically expand across the map, active research in technology and culture unlocks new potential, and competing leaders will pursue their own agendas based on their historical traits as you race for one of five ways to achieve victory in the game. See the marvels of your empire spread across the map like never before. Each city spans multiple tiles so you can custom build your cities to take full advantage of the local terrain. Unlock boosts that speed your civilizations progress through history. To advance more quickly, use your units to actively explore, develop your environment, and discover new cultures.', 39.99, 'https://cdn1.epicgames.com/cd14dcaa4f3443f19f7169a980559c62/offer/EGS_SidMeiersCivilizationVI_FiraxisGames_S1-2560x1440-2fcd1c150ac6d8cdc672ae042d2dd179.jpg', '2K Games', '2016-10-21', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (5, 'FIFA 25', 'The latest installment in the popular soccer series', 'EA SPORTS FC 25 gives you more ways to win for the club. Team up with friends in your favorite modes with the new 5v5 Rush, and manage your club to victory as FC IQ delivers more tactical control than ever before. Feel closer to the game with three cutting-edge HyperMotionV technologies driving realistic football motion and next-gen Cranium that brings player heads to life. Plus, experience the womens game like never before with a global league season structure including the Barclays Womens Super League and Google Pixel Frauen-Bundesliga for the first time, alongside the existing NWSL and Division 1 Arkema. Rush your way through Ultimate Team, Clubs, and Kick-Off with a new 5v5 experience built on the foundations of football. Play the beautiful game your way with Quick Subs, Blue Cards, and dedicated tactics as you lead your small-sided team to glory. Recruit the worlds best players to build your dream squad and compete in the most popular mode in football games.', 69.99, 'https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/3/2024/07/FC-25-Jude-6ac2309.jpg?quality=90&fit=700,466', 'EA Sports', '2024-09-27', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (6, 'Resident Evil 4', 'Survival horror in a European village', 'Survival horror has been redefined for a new generation with Resident Evil 4, a remake of the industry-defining masterpiece. Leon S. Kennedy is sent on a mission to rescue the U.S. Presidents daughter who has been kidnapped. Finding his way to a rural village in Europe, he faces new threats that are a departure from the traditional lumbering zombie enemies of the earlier instalments in the series. Leon must fight horrific new creatures infested by a new threat called Las Plagas and face off against an aggressive group of enemies including mind-controlled villagers that are tied to Los Illuminados, the mysterious cult behind the abduction. Reimagined gameplay - The game preserves the essence of the original while updating the gameplay, story and graphics. The new camera system and modernized controls, which bring it up to the same standards as Resident Evil 2 and Resident Evil 3, make for a deeper, more challenging gameplay experience. An iconic story - The game preserves the essence of the original while telling the story from a fresh perspective with the goal of bringing the world of the original Resident Evil 4 to life while offering a fresh take that appeals to fans of the series and newcomers alike.', 59.99, 'https://images.wallpapersden.com/image/download/resident-evil-4-remake-poster-cool_bW5qa2eUmZqaraWkpJRoaGllrWdma2U.jpg', 'Capcom', '2023-03-24', 25);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (7, 'Portal 2', 'Mind-bending puzzle game with portals', 'The sequel to 2007s Game of the Year, Portal 2 is a hilariously mind-bending adventure that challenges you to use wits over weaponry in a funhouse of diabolical science. Using a highly experimental portal device, youll once again face off against a lethally inventive, power-mad A.I. named GLaDOS. And this time you wont be alone. Meet an expanded cast of characters as you think your way through dangerous, never-before-seen areas of Aperture Laboratories. Break the laws of spatial physics in ways you never thought possible, with a wider variety of portal puzzles and an expansive story that spans a single player and co-operative game mode. In single player you play as Chell in her first moments since being revived from suspended animation at the end of the original game. Co-op mode pits two players as robots equipped with their own Portal guns working together to solve puzzles. The games two-player cooperative mode features its own entirely separate campaign with a unique story, test chambers, and two new player characters.', 19.99, 'https://rhapsodistreviews.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/portal-2-advertisement.jpg', 'Valve', '2011-04-19', 50);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (8, 'Gran Turismo 7', 'The ultimate realistic racing simulator', 'Whether youre a competitive or casual racer, collector, tuner, livery designer or photographer – find your line with a staggering collection of game modes including fan-favorites like GT Campaign, Arcade and Driving School. With the reintroduction of the legendary GT Simulation Mode, buy, tune, race and sell your way through a rewarding solo campaign as you unlock new cars and challenges. And if you love going head-to-head with others, hone your skills and compete in the GT Sport Mode. With over 420 cars available at Brand Central and the Used Car dealership from day one, Gran Turismo 7 recreates the look and feel of classic motors and bleeding-edge supercars alike in unparalleled detail. Each car handles differently and feels unique as you navigate over 90 track routes in dynamic weather conditions, including classic courses from GT history. Collect, tune, race and sell cars. Starting with a garage and a small amount of cash, buy used and Brand Central cars to race through different events.', 69.99, 'https://myhotposters.com/cdn/shop/products/mL6040_1024x1024.jpg?v=1748532231', 'Sony', '2022-03-04', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (9, 'Street Fighter 6', 'Next generation fighting game evolution', 'Powered by Capcoms proprietary RE ENGINE, Street Fighter 6 spans three distinct game modes, including World Tour, Fighting Ground and Battle Hub. The experience also includes innovative new gameplay features, plus enhanced visuals for every aspect of the game. Here comes a new challenger! Street Fighter 6 launches worldwide on June 2nd, 2023 and represents the next evolution of the Street Fighter series! Street Fighter 6 features three game modes: Fighting Ground, World Tour and Battle Hub. The first of these, Fighting Ground, comprises the traditional versus fighting modes as well as new and innovative modes. World Tour is a single-player immersive story mode where players can create their own avatar and walk in the shoes of a fighter. Lastly, Battle Hub is a new hub where players from around the world can engage in a variety of activities. The Drive System is the new core battle mechanic of Street Fighter 6 that enhances the characters offense and defense by using the Drive Gauge.', 59.99, 'https://www.streetfighter.com/6/assets/images/index/mv_edition_bg.jpg', 'Capcom', '2023-06-02', 10);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (10, 'The Sims 4', 'Create and control virtual lives', 'Unleash your imagination and create a unique world of Sims that is an expression of you! Explore and customize every detail from Sims to homes, and much more. Choose how Sims look, act, and dress. Determine how they will live out their lives. Experience the creativity, humor, escape, and the freedom to play with life like never before in The Sims 4! Create unique Sims - A variety of Sims are yours to personalize, each with distinct appearances, dynamic personalities, and inspiring aspirations. Control their mind, body, and heart. Play with Life - Control the rich and entertaining moments of your Sims lives from their relationships to their careers. Your choices shape their lives and drive their storylines. Build the Perfect Home - Effortlessly construct the home of your dreams with the rooms you design. Choose your favorite designs and amenities, customize the landscape, and add all the adorable objects your Sims need for their daily routines. The Gallery - Browse an ever-growing library of over 5 million community creations.', 39.99, 'https://myhotposters.com/cdn/shop/products/mL3370_large.jpg?v=1748534525', 'EA', '2014-09-02', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (11, 'Skyrim', 'Epic open-world fantasy RPG adventure', 'Winner of more than 200 Game of the Year Awards, The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim celebrates 10 years of adventuring in stunning detail. The Special Edition includes the critically acclaimed game and add-ons with all-new features like remastered art and effects, volumetric god rays, dynamic depth of field, screen-space reflections, and more. Epic Fantasy Reborn - The next chapter in the highly anticipated Elder Scrolls saga arrives from the makers of the 2006 and 2008 Games of the Year, Bethesda Game Studios. Skyrim reimagines and revolutionizes the open-world fantasy epic, bringing to life a complete virtual world open for you to explore any way you choose. Live another life, in another world - Play any type of character you can imagine, and do whatever you want; the legendary freedom of choice, storytelling, and adventure of The Elder Scrolls is realized like never before. Choose from hundreds of weapons, spells, and abilities. The new character system allows you to play any way you want and define yourself through your actions. You Are What You Play - An all-new engine brings to life a complete virtual world with rolling clouds, rugged mountains, bustling cities, lush fields, and ancient dungeons.', 39.99, 'https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-yzgoj/images/stencil/1280x1280/products/3221714/6208078/XPSMX5056__62906.1709693620.jpg?c=2', 'Bethesda', '2011-11-11', 30);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (12, 'Minecraft', 'Build and explore infinite blocky worlds', 'Minecraft is a game about placing blocks and going on adventures. Explore randomly generated worlds and build amazing things from the simplest of homes to the grandest of castles. Play in Creative Mode with unlimited resources or mine deep into the world in Survival Mode, crafting weapons and armor to fend off dangerous mobs. Create, explore and survive alone or with friends on mobile devices, Switch, Xbox One and Windows 10. Expand your game: Marketplace - Discover the latest community creations in the marketplace! Get unique maps, skins, and texture packs from your favorite creators. Slash commands - Tweak how the game plays: you can give items away, summon mobs, change the time of day, and more. Add-Ons - Customize your experience even further with free Add-Ons! If youre more tech-inclined, you can modify data-driven behaviors in the game to create new resource packs. Realms - Play with up to 10 friends cross-platform, anytime, anywhere on Realms, your own private server that we host for you.', 26.95, 'https://cdn.bhdw.net/im/minecraft-video-game-poster-wallpaper-115347_w635.webp', 'Mojang', '2011-11-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (13, 'Dark Souls III', 'Challenging action RPG with brutal combat', 'Dark Souls continues to push the boundaries with the latest, ambitious chapter in the critically-acclaimed and genre-defining series. As fires fade and the world falls into ruin, journey into a universe filled with more colossal enemies and environments. Players will be immersed into a world of epic atmosphere and darkness through faster gameplay and amplified combat intensity. Fans and newcomers alike will get lost in the games hallmark rewarding gameplay and immersive graphics. Now only embers remain Dive into a world of epic atmosphere and explore places where fires still burn. Only embers remain in these lands where flame represents hope and conflict. Your darkest journey yet - Confront towering enemies and immersive, stunningly realized locations. The most cunning traps and monstrous foes in series history await in meticulously designed levels. Mastering intense combat - From the onset of combat, your choices will be split-second life or death decisions. Use strategic swordplay to defeat foes and harness the power of pyromancy to scorch whatever stands in your way.', 59.99, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/91rTxm40jwL.jpg', 'FromSoftware', '2016-04-12', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (14, 'Stardew Valley', 'Peaceful farming and community life simulator', 'Youve inherited your grandfathers old farm plot in Stardew Valley. Armed with hand-me-down tools and a few coins, you set out to begin your new life. Can you learn to live off the land and turn these overgrown fields into a thriving home? It wont be easy. Ever since Joja Corporation came to town, the old ways of life have all but disappeared. The community center, once the towns most vibrant hub of activity, now lies in shambles. But the valley seems full of opportunity. With a little dedication, you might just be the one to restore Stardew Valley to greatness! Turn your overgrown field into a lively farm - Raise animals, grow crops, start an orchard, craft useful machines, and more! Become part of the local community - Befriend the towns residents, get married and start a family. Customize your farmer and home - Hundreds of options to choose from. Explore a vast, mysterious cave - Battle monsters, collect treasure, and delve ever deeper in search of new creatures. From fishing to mining, combat to crafting, youll discover a variety of ways to spend your time.', 14.99, 'https://www.cnet.com/a/img/resize/58ff37aa45da6cea1a99541a7c4d45e290c5c02a/hub/2023/06/27/d99fe5c1-0f47-4319-82fb-db7a43daa815/stardew-valley-key-art-1200x675.png?auto=webp&fit=crop&height=675&width=1200', 'ConcernedApe', '2016-02-26', 40);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (15, 'Cyberpunk 2077', 'Futuristic open-world RPG in Night City', 'Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure RPG set in the dark future of Night City — a dangerous megalopolis obsessed with power, glamor, and ceaseless body modification. You play as V, a cyberpunk mercenary wrapped up in a do-or-die fight for survival. With Phantom Liberty — a spy-thriller expansion — experience an incredible adventure of espionage and intrigue entwined with a story of war, loyalty, loss and love. Play your way - Build your legend through the choices you make and relationships you forge. Choose your lifepath from Nomad, Street Kid, or Corpo. Multiple play styles through deep RPG mechanics. Customize your cyberware and master your unique skillset to hack, shoot, and sneak your way through the dark underworld of Night City. An immersive open world - Explore the city of the dark future, one of the best open worlds in gaming. Meet compelling characters in Night City and beyond. Experience the world of Cyberpunk 2077 through the eyes of mercenaries, fixers, criminals and civilians alike.', 59.99, 'https://w0.peakpx.com/wallpaper/130/167/HD-wallpaper-cyberpunk-2077-e3-2019-poster.jpg', 'CD Projekt Red', '2020-12-10', 35);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (16, 'Red Dead Redemption 2', 'Epic Wild West outlaw adventure', 'America, 1899. The end of the Wild West era has begun. After a robbery goes badly wrong in the western town of Blackwater, Arthur Morgan and the Van der Linde gang are forced to flee. With federal agents and the best bounty hunters in the nation massing on their heels, the gang must rob, steal and fight their way across the rugged heartland of America in order to survive. As deepening internal divisions threaten to tear the gang apart, Arthur must make a choice between his own ideals and loyalty to the gang who raised him. From the creators of Grand Theft Auto V and Red Dead Redemption, Red Dead Redemption 2 is an epic tale of life in Americas unforgiving heartland. The games vast and atmospheric world will also provide the foundation for a brand new online multiplayer experience. With all new graphical and technical enhancements for deeper immersion, Red Dead Redemption 2 for PC takes full advantage of the power of the PC to bring every corner of this massive, rich and detailed world to life.', 59.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/featured/red-dead-redemption-2-hd-completo-ul4kvf03rfghk8p8.jpg', 'Rockstar Games', '2018-10-26', 15);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (17, 'The Witcher 3', 'Hunt monsters across a fantasy continent', 'You are Geralt of Rivia, mercenary monster slayer. Before you stands a war-torn, monster-infested continent you can explore at will. Your current contract? Tracking down Crixion, the Child of Prophecy, a living weapon that can alter the shape of the world. The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt is a story-driven open world RPG set in a visually stunning fantasy universe full of meaningful choices and impactful consequences. In The Witcher you play as the professional monster hunter Geralt of Rivia tasked with finding a child of prophecy in a vast open world rich with merchant cities, viking pirate islands, dangerous mountain passes, and forgotten caverns to explore. Play as a highly trained monster slayer for hire - Trained from early childhood and mutated to gain superhuman skills, strength and reflexes, witchers are a counterbalance to the monster-infested world in which they live. Gruesomely destroy foes as a professional monster hunter armed with a range of upgradeable weapons, mutating potions and combat magic. Hunt down a wide variety of exotic monsters from savage beasts prowling the mountain passes to cunning supernatural predators lurking in the shadows of densely populated towns.', 39.99, 'https://forums.cdprojektred.com/index.php?attachments/witcher_3_next_gen-1920x1080-rgb-en-png.11244274/', 'CD Projekt Red', '2015-05-19', 25);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (18, 'Baldurs Gate 3', 'Epic D&D adventure in Forgotten Realms', 'Gather your party, and return to the Forgotten Realms in a tale of fellowship and betrayal, sacrifice and survival, and the lure of absolute power. Mysterious abilities are awakening inside you, drawn from a Mind Flayer parasite planted in your brain. Resist, and turn darkness against itself. Or embrace corruption, and become ultimate evil. From the creators of Divinity: Original Sin 2 comes a next-generation RPG, set in the world of Dungeons and Dragons. Choose from 12 classes and 11 races from the D&D Players Handbook and create your own identity, or play as an Origin hero with a hand-crafted background. Or play as the Dark Urge, a fully customisable Origin hero with their own unique mechanics and story. Whoever you choose to be, adventure, loot, battle and romance your way across the Forgotten Realms and beyond. Gather your party and return to the Forgotten Realms. All the choices matter in the award-winning RPG adventure. BG3 is based on D&D 5E. All the iconic D&D classes and races are available along with all the familiar spells and items from the tabletop game.', 59.99, 'https://www.psu.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Baldurs-Gate-3-PS5-Wallpapers-01.jpg', 'Larian Studios', '2023-08-03', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (19, 'Hades', 'Escape the Underworld in roguelike action', 'Defy the god of the dead as you hack and slash out of the Underworld in this rogue-like dungeon crawler from the creators of Bastion, Transistor, and Pyre. A Rogue-Like Dungeon Crawler - Battle out of hell in an ever-shifting dungeon. Each time you play you will find new surprises and the challenge is never the same. Wield the Powers and Mythic Weapons of Olympus - The Olympians have your back! Meet Zeus, Athena, Poseidon, and many more, and choose from their dozens of powerful Blessings that enhance your abilities. Gods, monsters, and Greek mythology come to life in Supergiant Games vivid hand-painted art style. Our critically acclaimed composer has crafted a blood-pumping score that brings out the best of the games fast-paced action, and brings you closer to the heart of the story. New surprises await each time you delve into the ever-shifting Underworld. Battle beyond the Underworld using dark sorcery to take on greater challenges. The rich, atmospheric presentation and unique melding of gameplay and narrative that weve been developing in our games is here in full force.', 24.99, 'https://images2.alphacoders.com/115/1151800.png', 'Supergiant Games', '2020-09-17', 20);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (20, 'Hollow Knight', 'Explore a haunting insect kingdom underground', 'Forge your own path in Hollow Knight! An epic action adventure through a vast ruined kingdom of insects and heroes. Explore twisting caverns, battle tainted creatures and befriend bizarre bugs, all in a classic, hand-drawn 2D style. A Vast, Haunting World - Explore Hallownest, an ancient underground kingdom of insects and heroes. Encounter over 150 enemies! Evolve with powerful new skills and abilities! Classic Side-Scrolling Action - Leap and dash your way through caverns full of twisting passages and dark secrets. Forge your own path in a world that changes with the actions you take! Epic Boss Fights - Test your skills against 30+ epic bosses. Learn their attack patterns, master their unique behaviours, and discover their weaknesses! Chart Your Journey Through the Wilderness - Take on an all-new quest in a strange land. Discover new friends and foes! Chart your journey with extensive mapping tools. Beautiful Art and Music - Traditional hand-drawn animation brings the characters and world of Hollow Knight to life in vivid, moody detail.', 14.99, 'https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/ar_16:9,c_lpad,w_1240/b_white/f_auto/q_auto/store/software/switch/70010000003208/4643fb058642335c523910f3a7910575f56372f612f7c0c9a497aaae978d3e51', 'Team Cherry', '2017-02-24', 30);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (21, 'Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice', 'Brutal samurai action in feudal Japan', 'Carve your own clever path to vengeance in the award winning adventures from developer FromSoftware. In Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice you are the ''one-armed wolf'', a disgraced and disfigured warrior rescued from the brink of death. Bound to protect a young lord who is the descendant of an ancient bloodline, you become the target of many vicious enemies, including the dangerous Ashina clan. When the young lord is captured, nothing will stop you on a perilous quest to regain your honor, not even death itself. Explore late 1500s Sengoku Japan, a brutal period of constant life and death conflict. Take Revenge. Restore Your Honor. Kill Ingeniously. Unique Combat - Your enemies are numerous and powerful. Prosthetic Tools add a new strategic dimension to the battle system. Resurrection - When death comes, your enemies will celebrate their triumph. Don''t let them. The power of the Dragon''s Heritage flows through you. Rise up and come back from death to take your revenge. Experience the Latest FromSoftware Adventure - Developers of the critically acclaimed Dark Souls series and Bloodborne turn their attention to Sengoku era Japan.', 59.99, 'https://wallpapercg.com/media/ts_orig/19904.webp', 'FromSoftware', '2019-03-22', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (22, 'Monster Hunter: World', 'Hunt giant monsters in living ecosystems', 'Welcome to a new world! Take on the role of a hunter and slay ferocious monsters in a living, breathing ecosystem where you can use the landscape and its diverse inhabitants to get the upper hand. Hunt alone or in co-op with up to three other players, and use materials collected from fallen foes to craft new gear and take on even bigger, badder beasts! Battle gigantic monsters in epic locales. As a hunter, you''ll take on quests to hunt monsters in a variety of habitats. Take down these monsters and receive materials that you can use to create stronger weapons and armor in order to hunt even more dangerous monsters. A Living, Breathing Ecosystem - Utilize the surrounding environment and wildlife to your advantage in battle or become hindered by the hazards they present. As a hunter, you must use your cunning to survive. Global Simultaneous Release - For the first time in the series, Monster Hunter World will release worldwide on the same date. Online Drop-In Multiplayer - When the battle is too daunting to take on single-handedly, hail up to three other hunters to assist during quests by sending up a SOS flare.', 29.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/2440x1440-monster-hunter-world-background-2440-x-1440-r8l6nhevzef9mzbz.jpg', 'Capcom', '2018-01-26', 35);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (23, 'Doom Eternal', 'Fast-paced demon slaying FPS action', 'Hell''s armies have invaded Earth. Become the Slayer in an epic single-player campaign to conquer demons across dimensions and stop the final destruction of humanity. The Only Thing they Fear... Is You. Experience the ultimate combination of speed and power in DOOM Eternal - the next leap in push-forward, first-person combat. Armed with a shoulder-mounted flamethrower, retractable wrist-mounted blade, upgraded guns and mods, and abilities, you''re faster, stronger, and more versatile than ever. Take what you need from your enemies: Glory kill for extra health, incinerate for armor, and chainsaw demons to stock up on ammo. These tools are the key to your survival and becoming the ultimate demon-slayer. Slaying is the Best Way to Stay Alive - Obliterate more demons than ever before, each with unique attacks and abilities. Unholy Trinity - Take your campaign experience to a new level with the additional player-versus-player mode. A fully-armed DOOM Slayer faces off against two player-controlled demons. Expand Your Experience - Enjoy a vast array of content including story-driven campaigns, multiplayer, and numerous game modes.', 39.99, 'https://images.wallpapersden.com/image/download/doom-eternal-8k-poster_a21ra22UmZqaraWkpJRsbWdprWltbGw.jpg', 'id Software', '2020-03-20', 40);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (24, 'Divinity: Original Sin 2', 'Tactical RPG with deep combat system', 'The Divine is dead. The Void approaches. And the powers lying dormant within you are soon to awaken. The battle for Divinity has begun. Choose wisely and trust sparingly; darkness lurks within every heart. Who will you be? A flesh-eating Elf, an Imperial Lizard or an Undead, risen from the grave? Discover how the world reacts differently to who - or what - you are. Gather your party - Create your own characters and control a full party! Co-op and competitive multiplayer modes with up to 4 players let you take your adventure online. Master deep, tactical combat - Featuring a revamped battle system, Divinity: Original Sin II offers an immersive experience where skill and creativity matter more than character level. Over 200 skills to choose from and combine! Choose Your Path - Unlimited freedom to explore and experiment. Go anywhere, unleash your imagination, and see how the game reacts. Unravel an epic story - An expansive campaign filled with unforgettable characters, meaningful choices, and impactful consequences. The Definitive Edition includes countless improvements based on player feedback.', 44.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/120/1204667.png', 'Larian Studios', '2017-09-14', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (25, 'Terraria', 'Dig, build, and fight in 2D', 'Dig, fight, explore, build! Nothing is impossible in this action-packed adventure game. The world is your canvas and the ground itself is your paint. Grab your tools and go! Make weapons to fight off a variety of enemies in numerous biomes. Dig deep underground to find accessories, money, and other useful things. Gather resources to create everything you need to make the world your own. Build a house, a fort, or even a castle. People will move in to live there and perhaps even sell you different wares to assist you on your journey. But beware, there are even more challenges awaiting you... Are you up to the task? Key Features: Sandbox Play - Randomly generated worlds. Free Content Updates - The team at Re-Logic continue to release new content for free. Multiplayer - Play with up to 7 friends online or on local WiFi. Over 5000 Items to Craft - Craft a Minishark, or the mightiest blade in all the world. NPCs - Youre not the only person in the world! Over 25 friendly characters can move into your towns and villages.', 9.99, 'https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/409210/ss_9aa3139e3f335121f05d530ecab15b23cc9116c3.1920x1080.jpg?t=1602690120', 'Re-Logic', '2011-05-16', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (26, 'Cities: Skylines', 'Build and manage your dream city', 'Cities: Skylines is a modern take on the classic city simulation. The game introduces new game play elements to realize the thrill and hardships of creating and maintaining a real city whilst expanding on some well-established tropes of the city building experience. From the makers of the Cities in Motion franchise, the game boasts a fully realized transport system. It also includes the ability to mod the game to suit your play style as a fine counter balance to the layered and challenging simulation. Multi-tiered and challenging simulation - Constructing your city from the ground up is easy to learn, but hard to master. Build Efficiently - Multi-layered simulation allows you to understand the many choices made by the citizens in your city. Local traffic simulation - Citizens have their own vehicles, which they use to navigate through the city. Districts and Policies - Not only can you designate zones, but you can also customize how your city looks. Extensive modding support - Build it your way. Cities: Skylines is built with modding in mind.', 29.99, 'https://gaming-cdn.com/images/products/519/616x353/cities-skylines-pc-mac-gioco-steam-cover.jpg?v=1662469928', 'Paradox', '2015-03-10', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (27, 'Total War: Warhammer III', 'Epic fantasy strategy with massive battles', 'The cataclysmic conclusion to the Total War: WARHAMMER trilogy is here. Rally your forces and step into the Realm of Chaos, a dimension of mind-bending horror where the very fate of the world will be decided. Will you conquer your Daemons… or command them? Each choice will shape the reality-shattering conflict to come. Wield the Power of the Chaos Gods - Play as a Daemon Prince and pledge your allegiance to one of the four Chaos Gods. Conquer with Mortal Champions - Lead the Daemons of Khorne, Nurgle, Slaanesh and Tzeentch into battle. Discover Seven Unique Races - Each race has its own playstyle and campaign mechanics. The Biggest Total War Ever - The Combined Map of Immortal Empires features all three games combined into one massive experience containing over 280 playable Legendary Lords. Epic Real-Time Battles - Unleash the full power of your strategy on the real-time battlefield. Command thousands of troops in spectacular clashes across fantastical war-torn lands. The Deep Campaign Strategy - Choose your faction and embark on a unique narrative campaign.', 59.99, 'https://gaming-cdn.com/images/products/12676/orig/total-war-warhammer-iii-champions-of-chaos-mac-pc-gioco-steam-europe-cover.jpg?v=1683621994', 'Creative Assembly', '2022-02-17', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (28, 'Forza Horizon 5', 'Open-world racing adventure in Mexico', 'Your Ultimate Horizon Adventure awaits! Explore the vibrant and ever-evolving open world landscapes of Mexico with limitless, fun driving action in hundreds of the world''s greatest cars. Lead breathtaking expeditions across the vibrant and ever-evolving open world landscapes of Mexico with limitless, fun driving action in hundreds of the worlds greatest cars. Explore a World of Striking Contrast and Beauty. Discover living deserts, lush jungles, historic cities, hidden ruins, pristine beaches, vast canyons and a towering snow-capped volcano. Immerse yourself in a deep campaign with hundreds of challenges that reward you for engaging in the activities you love. Meet new characters and choose the outcomes of their Horizon Story missions. Take on Horizon Arcade for a continuing series of fun, over-the-top challenges. Team up with others to compete in The Eliminator battle royale. Create your own expressions of fun with the new EventLab gameplay toolset including custom races, challenges, stunts, and entirely new game modes. Customize your cars in more ways than ever before.', 59.99, 'https://images.alphacoders.com/116/1168382.jpg', 'Playground Games', '2021-11-09', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (29, 'Disco Elysium', 'Detective RPG with unprecedented player choice', 'Disco Elysium - The Final Cut is the definitive edition of the groundbreaking role playing game. You''re a detective with a unique skill system at your disposal and a whole city block to carve your path across. Interrogate unforgettable characters, crack murders or take bribes. Become a hero or an absolute disaster of a human being. Unprecedented freedom of choice - Intimidate, sweet-talk, resort to violence, write poetry, sing karaoke, dance like a beast or solve the meaning of life. Disco Elysium is the most faithful representation of desktop role playing ever attempted in video games. Countless tools for role playing - A revolutionary dialogue system with 24 mind attributes you can internalize gives you endless ways to roleplay. Detective, apocalypse cop, art cop, gym cop, sorry cop - be whatever kind of cop you want to be. A vast world to explore - The city of Revachol is yours for the taking, one small piece at a time. From the streets to the beaches investigate a massive murder mystery and find your own version of the truth.', 39.99, 'https://images.ft.com/v3/image/raw/https%3A%2F%2Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%2Fproduction%2Ff0808b5a-fe30-4d7f-9331-e36a521b7734.png?source=next-article&fit=scale-down&quality=highest&width=700&dpr=1', 'ZA/UM', '2019-10-15', 45);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (30, 'Subnautica', 'Survive and explore alien ocean depths', 'Descend into the depths of an alien underwater world filled with wonder and peril. Craft equipment, pilot submarines and out-smart wildlife to explore lush coral reefs, volcanoes, cave systems, and more - all while trying to survive. You have crash-landed on an alien ocean world, and the only way to go is down. Subnauticas oceans range from sun drenched shallow coral reefs to treacherous deep-sea trenches, lava fields, and bio-luminescent underwater rivers. Manage your oxygen supply as you explore kelp forests, plateaus, reefs, and winding cave systems. The water teems with life: Some of it helpful, much of it harmful. Scavenge, Craft, and Survive - After crash landing in your Life Pod, the clock is ticking to find water, food, and to develop the equipment you need to explore. Collect resources from the ocean around you. Craft knives, lights, diving gear, and personal water craft. Venture deeper and further form to find rarer resources, allowing you to craft more advanced items. Construct Underwater Habitats - Build bases on the sea floor.', 29.99, 'https://cdnb.artstation.com/p/assets/images/images/008/300/939/large/fox3d-entertainment-7.jpg?1511865717', 'Unknown Worlds', '2018-01-23', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (31, 'Celeste', 'Challenging platformer about climbing a mountain', 'Help Madeline survive her inner demons on her journey to the top of Celeste Mountain, in this super-tight platformer from the creators of TowerFall. Brave hundreds of hand-crafted challenges, uncover devious secrets, and piece together the mystery of the mountain. A Narrative-Driven, Single-Player Adventure - A story of self-discovery, anxiety, and personal struggles, wrapped in a super tight platforming game. Hundreds of Handcrafted Challenges - Explore a massive mountain with new surprises around every corner. Brutal B-Side Chapters - Unlock super tough alternate versions of levels after completing the main story. Meet Madeline and survive her inner demons on her journey to the top of Celeste Mountain. The controls are simple and accessible - simply jump, air-dash, and climb - but with layers of expressive depth to master, where every death is a lesson. Lightning-fast respawns keep you climbing as you uncover the mysteries of the mountain and brave its many perils. This is it, Madeline. Just breathe. You can do this.', 19.99, 'https://images7.alphacoders.com/901/thumb-1920-901149.png', 'Maddy Makes Games', '2018-01-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (32, 'Dead Cells', 'Roguelike action in an evolving castle', 'Dead Cells is a rogue-lite, metroidvania inspired action-platformer. You''ll explore a sprawling, ever-changing castle... assuming you''re able to fight your way past its keepers in 2D souls-lite combat. No checkpoints. Kill, die, learn, repeat. Interconnected levels and progressive unlocking of access to the island provides you with a real incentive to explore your surroundings. RogueVania: Intense 2D action with the adrenaline pumping threat of permadeath in a castle full of cuddly creatures. Souls-like combat: Pattern-based bosses and minions, weapons and spells with unique gameplay. Roll roll roll your boat gently down the stream. Nonlinear progression: Sewers, Ossuary or Ramparts? Once unlocked, special permanent abilities allow you to access new paths to reach your objective. Opt for the path that suits your current build, your play style or just your mood. Exploration: Secret rooms, hidden passages, charming landscapes. Take a moment to stroll the towers and breath in that fresh sea mist infused air.', 24.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/dead-cells-game-artwork-fa3u15j4bjv82pjc.jpg', 'Motion Twin', '2018-08-07', 30);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (33, 'Control', 'Supernatural action in a shifting building', 'After a secretive agency in New York is invaded by an otherworldly threat, you become the new Director struggling to regain Control. From developer Remedy Entertainment, this supernatural third-person action-adventure will challenge you to master the combination of supernatural abilities, modifiable loadouts, and reactive environments while fighting through a deep and unpredictable world. Control is Jesse Fadens story. The main plot focuses on her personal search for answers as she grows into the role of the Director. The world of Control has its own story, as do the allies Jesse meets along the way. Side-quests and Secrets are everywhere. Jesse works with other Bureau agents, decodes cryptic ciphers and discovers strange Bureau experiments. Explore diverse environments and shifting architecture in a deep unpredictable world, set within a sprawling New York building. Define your playstyle by integrating supernatural abilities, upgrades, and modifiable loadouts. Harness dynamic environmental destruction for exciting combat possibilities.', 29.99, 'https://wallpaper.forfun.com/fetch/f4/f4f42a6cff7722a1d95b7c5c5e18d435.jpeg', 'Remedy', '2019-08-27', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (34, 'Resident Evil Village', 'First-person horror in a mysterious village', 'Experience survival horror like never before in the eighth major installment in the Resident Evil franchise - Resident Evil Village. With detailed graphics, intense first-person action and masterful storytelling, the terror has never felt more realistic. Set a few years after the horrifying events in the critically acclaimed Resident Evil 7 biohazard, the all-new storyline begins with Ethan Winters and his wife Mia living peacefully in a new location, free from their past nightmares. Just as they are building their new life together, tragedy befalls them once again. First-Person Action - Players will assume the role of Ethan Winters and experience every up-close battle and horrifying encounter from the first-person perspective. The Mysterious Village - The game takes place years after the horrific events of Resident Evil 7. The enigmatic Umbrella Corporation has disappeared. A New Chapter of Terror - The next generation of survival horror rises. From world-renowned game developer Capcom, Resident Evil Village delivers a terrifyingly beautiful experience.', 59.99, 'https://www.psu.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/resident-evil-village-ps5-wallpapers-09.png', 'Capcom', '2021-05-07', 20);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (35, 'Hitman 3', 'Stealth assassination across exotic locations', 'Death Awaits. HITMAN 3 is the dramatic conclusion to the World of Assassination trilogy. Become Agent 47 and experience the most intimate and professional contract killing experience in the series. Travel the globe and track your targets across exotic sandbox locations in HITMAN 3. From sun-drenched streets to dark and dangerous rainforests, nowhere is safe from the worlds most creative assassin, Agent 47. Think deadly and plan carefully. Improvise and use the environment to your advantage. The Hitman Trilogy is the culmination of over 20 years of Hitman development and features all the content from Hitman 1, 2, and 3 in one package. If you have purchased HITMAN 1 or HITMAN 2, you can bring your existing progress and purchases into HITMAN 3. Agent 47 Returns - A Dramatic Conclusion: Experience a globetrotting adventure and visit meticulously detailed locations that are packed full of creative opportunities. Play Your Way - With a wide range of tools and weapons at your disposal, you have complete freedom to approach each mission exactly as you please.', 59.99, 'https://cdn1.epicgames.com/ed55aa5edc5941de92fd7f64de415793/offer/Landscape-2560x1440-1f18287d356309156374725e80c2fc6a.jpg', 'IO Interactive', '2021-01-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (36, 'Dark and Darker - Legendary Status', 'Hardcore fantasy dungeon PvPvE extraction', 'An unforgiving hardcore fantasy FPS dungeon PvPvE adventure. Band together with your friends and use your courage, wits, and cunning to uncover mythical treasures, defeat gruesome monsters, while staying one step ahead of the other devious treasure-hunters. Once you''ve plundered your riches, now comes the hard part, getting out alive. Discover abundant loot to empower your character and to bring back to camp. But beware, death is final and you will lose everything. Defeat monstrous creatures, loot treasure, and escape the horrors of the dungeon. Play Solo or with a Party of up to three. Choose from eight distinct classes. Fighter, Barbarian, Rogue, Ranger, Wizard, Cleric, Bard, or Warlock. Master each class through their unique perks and skill kits. Extract with treasure and unlock new gear. Buy, trade, and sell your loot. Legendary Status grants access to exclusive in-game perks and bonuses to enhance your dungeon-delving experience.', 49.99, 'https://gaming-cdn.com/images/products/13354/orig/dark-and-darker-pc-steam-cover.jpg?v=1760019213', 'IRONMACE', '2024-06-07', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (37, 'Valheim', 'Viking survival adventure in procedural purgatory', 'A brutal exploration and survival game for 1-10 players, set in a procedurally-generated purgatory inspired by viking culture. Battle, build, and conquer your way to a saga worthy of Odin''s patronage! Explore a world shrouded in mystery. From meadows to mountains, thick forests, and dark swamps, Valheim has a massive world that is procedurally generated, ensuring that no two playthroughs are ever the same. Build mighty longhouses and fine buildings. From a simple shack to a mighty stone castle, lay down foundations and build the settlement of your dreams. All structure pieces support each other, creating a dynamic structural integrity system. Fight fearsome creatures. Hunt down beasts for their hides and meat. Gather resources and craft weapons and armor to venture into more dangerous places. Sail the open seas. Explore a massive world by land and sea. Build mighty longships and venture out on the ocean to discover new lands and resources. Co-op PvE (2-10 Players) - Whether you want to brave the lands alone or venture with trusted allies, Valheim supports co-op.', 19.99, 'https://xboxwire.thesourcemediaassets.com/sites/2/2023/03/Valheim-Hero-0903ad6c1703d0662430.jpg', 'Iron Gate', '2021-02-02', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (38, 'No Mans Sky', 'Explore infinite procedurally generated universe', 'No Man''s Sky is a game about exploration and survival in an infinite procedurally generated universe. Explore endless unique worlds, each with their own lifeforms, ecosystems and challenges. Discover ancient alien artifacts, mysterious worlds and engage in epic space combat. Build bases and command freighters to mine valuable resources, craft new technologies and defend yourself in combat. Team up with friends or explore alone in this vast universe. Explore - Explore an infinite universe. Every planet, creature, tree, and sun in this game is unique. Survive - Battle against fierce creatures and aggressive pirates. Navigate dangerous environments filled with violent storms. Build - Create signature bases, customizing layouts and appearance. Construct elaborate structures reaching to the clouds. Craft - Construct new technologies and upgrade weapons, tools, ships and equipment. Trade - Become a wealthy trader, or save up for that enormous capital freighter. Join The Community - Join other travelers online, team up to explore together or race to be the first to find elusive treasures.', 59.99, 'https://gameranx.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/No-Mans-Sky-1080-Wallpaper.jpg', 'Hello Games', '2016-08-09', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (39, 'Deep Rock Galactic', 'Co-op dwarven mining in alien caves', 'Work together as a team of dwarven space miners to dig, explore, and fight your way through a massive cave system filled with hordes of deadly aliens and valuable resources. You will need to rely on your teammates if you want to survive the most hostile cave systems in the galaxy! 4 Player Co-op - Work together as a team to dig, explore, and fight your way through a massive cave system. 4 Unique Classes - Pick the right class for the job. Drill through solid rock, light up the darkness, provide defensive structures or call in vital supplies. Fully Destructible Environments - Destroy everything around you to reach your goal. There is no set path so you can complete your mission your way. Procedurally Generated Cave Network - Explore a network of procedurally generated cave systems filled with enemies to kill and riches to collect. High-Tech Weapons and Tools - Dwarves know what they need to bring to get the job done. Kill alien bugs with the most lethal weapons and gadgets. Rock and Stone! The motto that bonds all dwarves together in their dangerous line of work.', 29.99, 'https://images.steamusercontent.com/ugc/5090788033229140426/840DFFE8246D5E50105CE7B48381683BA94D08A0/?imw=5000&imh=5000&ima=fit&impolicy=Letterbox&imcolor=%23000000&letterbox=false', 'Ghost Ship Games', '2020-05-13', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (40, 'Risk of Rain 2', 'Chaotic roguelike shooter on alien planet', 'Escape a chaotic alien planet by fighting through hordes of frenzied monsters – with your friends, or on your own. Combine loot in surprising ways and master each character until you become the havoc you feared upon your first crash landing. No run will ever be the same with randomized stages, enemies, bosses, and items. Play by yourself, or team up with up to four friends to fight your way through hordes of monsters, unlock new loot, and find a way to escape the planet. With classic roguelike mechanics and Risk of Rain''s unique loot system, no two runs will feel the same. Discover the lore behind Commando, Huntress, MUL-T, Engineer, and more as you dive deeper into the story of Risk of Rain 2. Play through multiple challenging stages, unlocking secrets and new characters with each completion. Over 75 items to unlock and infinitely combine them for a unique experience each run. Over 11 playable character classes, each with their own unique skills and playstyles. Countless combinations ensure each run is unique.', 24.99, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XKa4SWYz2HQ/hq720.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEhCK4FEIIDSFryq4qpAxMIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJD&rs=AOn4CLDGe2_dLzFdqJ-wb7XAku_o3pP8MA', 'Hopoo Games', '2020-08-11', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (41, 'Phasmophobia', 'Co-op psychological ghost hunting horror', 'Phasmophobia is a 4 player online co-op psychological horror. Paranormal activity is on the rise and its up to you and your team to use all the ghost hunting equipment at your disposal in order to gather as much evidence as you can. Immersive Experience - Realistic graphics and sounds as well as a minimal user interface ensure a totally immersive experience that will keep you on your toes. Use your ghost hunting equipment to find and record evidence to sell to a ghost removal team. Play Alone or With Friends - Can be played by a minimum of 1 and maximum of 4 players. Over 20 Different Types of Ghosts - Over 20 different types of ghosts all with unique traits meaning each investigation will be different. Equipment to Find Evidence - Use well known ghost hunting equipment such as EMF Readers, Spirit Boxes, Thermometers and Night Vision Cameras to find clues and gather as much paranormal evidence as you can. Communicate With Spirits - The ghosts are listening! Use the Ouija Board or Spirit Box to communicate with the ghosts.', 13.99, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/GskxFBjXgAEPW82.jpg:large', 'Kinetic Games', '2020-09-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (42, 'Left 4 Dead 2', 'Co-op zombie shooter in Deep South', 'Set in the zombie apocalypse, Left 4 Dead 2 is the highly anticipated sequel to the award-winning Left 4 Dead. This co-operative action horror FPS takes you and your friends through the cities, swamps and cemeteries of the Deep South, from Savannah to New Orleans across five expansive campaigns. New Survivors. New Locations. New Weapons. New Infected - Four new Survivors face off against five new Special Infected, including the horrific Spitter, the controlling Jockey, and the Charger. New AI Director 2.0 - Advanced technology dubbed "The AI Director 2.0" dynamically creates the ultimate FPS battle horror experience. The Director 2.0 tailors the flow and intensity of gameplay according to how the players are faring. New Weapons and Items - You''ll get to unleash a variety of zombie-killing weaponry, from chainsaws to shotguns to the versatile AK-47. Grab some adrenaline or defibrillators or tear apart infected with melee weapons like the gory chainsaw. Cooperative Campaigns - Play through five extensive new campaigns, or take on endless challenges in the Survival mode.', 9.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/left-4-dead-2-survivors-8z3pb5bfrs2mk2pm.jpg', 'Valve', '2009-11-17', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (43, 'Remnant II', 'Co-op action RPG across terrifying worlds', 'Remnant II pits survivors of humanity against new deadly creatures and god-like bosses across terrifying worlds. Play solo or co-op with two other friends to explore the depths of the unknown to stop an evil from destroying reality itself. To succeed, players will need to rely on their own skills and those of their team to overcome the toughest challenges and to stave off humanity''s extinction. Unimaginable Worlds - Journey through dynamic and dangerous worlds alone or with friends to stop evil from destroying reality itself. Endless Replayability - Branching quest lines, augments, crafting, and loot rewards create diverse builds and overpowered playstyles that change with each playthrough. New Dangers at Every Turn - Overcome cunning enemies and huge bosses throughout dynamically generated dungeons and areas. Return to a reimagined world with branching paths to explore. Advanced Archetype Class System - Define your playstyle with unique classes and customization. Try different combinations to overcome any challenge. Seamless Co-op multiplayer - Adventure alone or call in allies for co-op support in combat.', 49.99, 'https://image.api.playstation.com/vulcan/ap/rnd/202402/1420/08454bafeab3eccfe8cb52cf53f6fc2e47c099810b21ab3c.jpg', 'Gunfire Games', '2023-07-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (44, 'Satisfactory', 'First-person factory building on alien planet', 'Satisfactory is a first-person open-world factory building game with a dash of exploration and combat. Play alone or with friends, explore an alien planet, create multi-story factories, and enter conveyor belt heaven! Conquer nature by building massive factories across the land. Expand wherever and however you want. The planet is filled with valuable natural resources just waiting to be utilized. As an employee of FICSIT it''s your duty to make sure they come to good use. Automate vehicles to bring your buildings the resources they need. No conveyor belt spaghetti necessary – though very awesome if you wish. Explore and exploit the planet for natural resources. Utilize natural wonders like gas geysers to fuel your expansion. Build Vertically - Stack your buildings on top of each other to get a real skyscraper feeling! Automate Everything - Automate transportation of materials, production and item sorters. Online Co-op - Build factories together with your friends! Jump in and out of each others games.', 29.99, 'https://wallpaper.forfun.com/fetch/91/915ef00645061a0d714d1f913a38ed9b.jpeg?w=1200&r=0.5625', 'Coffee Stain', '2024-09-10', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (45, 'Lethal Company', 'Co-op horror scavenging on abandoned moons', 'A co-op horror about scavenging at abandoned moons to sell scrap to the Company. You are a contracted worker for the Company. Your job is to collect scrap from abandoned, industrialized moons to meet the Company''s profit quota. You can use the cash you earn to travel to new moons with higher risks and rewards—or you can buy fancy suits and decorations for your ship. Experience nature, scanning any creature you find to add them to your bestiary. Explore the wondrous outdoors and rummage through their derelict, steel and concrete underbellies. Just never miss the quota. Use the terminal to keep track of your crew''s vital signs and to order useful items to support and survive on the deadly moons. Work together with up to 4 friends and explore the moons in a cooperative fashion. Talk about strategies, call for help, and navigate the complexities of communication and cooperation or die alone in the dark. Watch your step as the Company won''t cover your insurance.', 9.99, 'https://images2.alphacoders.com/134/1344905.jpeg', 'Zeekerss', '2023-10-23', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (46, 'Rust', 'Brutal multiplayer survival on hostile island', 'The only aim in Rust is to survive. Everything wants you to die - the island''s wildlife and other inhabitants, the environment, other survivors. Do whatever it takes to last another night. Awaken naked and alone on the shores of a mysterious island. Armed with only a rock and a torch, you must brave natural dangers and fight off aggressive wildlife - or become prey. Build a shelter, hunt for food, and craft tools and weapons to defend yourself. Form alliances or wage war with other players as you work to survive in this harsh, unforgiving world. Craft items and buildings. The crafting system allows for a wide variety of items and structures. Start Out With Nothing - Gather materials to craft shelter and tools. Research Items - Take items you find and research them to unlock them in your crafting menu. Danger Around Every Corner - Fight or befriend other players, animals, and the elements. Base Building and Raiding - Build massive fortresses or raid those of your enemies.', 39.99, 'https://images.steamusercontent.com/ugc/709652207099877539/7144676E84ADC21366F1328D0C049F3E62E58B4B/', 'Facepunch Studios', '2018-02-08', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (47, 'Palworld', 'Creature collecting survival with base building', 'Fight, farm, build and work alongside mysterious creatures called Pals in this brand new multiplayer, open-world survival and crafting game! In this world, you can peacefully coexist with mysterious creatures known as Pals or risk your life to drive off a ruthless poaching syndicate. Pals can be used to fight, breed, help with building, or work in factories. You can even sell them or butcher them to eat! In an age of gun and sword, journey alone or team up with friends as you adventure across the land with your Pals. Life in Palworld - Make your Pals work overtime to generate money. Survival in a Harsh World - Food is scarce. You must find ways to make your Pals work in order to survive. Mount and Explore - Fly, swim, dig or ride across land on your Pals. Building and Automation - With the help of Pals, you can build various structures from houses to factories. Multiplayer - Supports cooperative play for up to 32 players.', 29.99, 'https://i.pinimg.com/736x/22/a2/67/22a267699325a8e7b579c0265a5e6920.jpg', 'Pocketpair', '2024-01-19', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (48, 'Sons of the Forest', 'Survival horror on cannibal-infested island', 'Sent to find a missing billionaire on a remote island, you find yourself in a cannibal-infested hellscape. Craft, build, and struggle to survive, alone or with friends, in this terrifying new open-world survival horror simulator. Experience complete freedom to tackle the world how you want. You decide what you do, where to go and how best to survive. Build and Craft - Feel every interaction; break sticks to make fires. Use an axe to cut out windows and floors. Build a small shelter or a seaside compound. Seasons - Complete with changing weather patterns, temps affect your abilities. Survive - Fight demons both above and below ground. Kelvin and Virginia - A super-smart AI companion who helps you and a mysterious three-legged, three-armed creature. Co-op Multiplayer - Survive together with up to 8 friends on the island. Share items, work together to build, explore, and survive.', 29.99, 'https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/sons-of-the-forest.jpg?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop', 'Endnight Games', '2024-02-22', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (49, 'Factorio', 'Automated factory building and optimization', 'Factorio is a game about building and creating automated factories to produce items of increasing complexity, within an infinite 2D world. Use your imagination to design your factory, combine simple elements into ingenious structures, and finally protect it from the creatures who don''t really like you. The game is very stable and optimized for building massive factories. You can create your own maps, write mods in Lua, or play with friends via Multiplayer. Automate Everything - From mining to smelting, from production to research, there is an incredible array of machines at your disposal. Vast Technology Tree - Through research, you will progressively unlock new buildings and ways to automate production. Multiplayer - Cooperative and competitive multiplayer, supports 50+ players. Fight Against Aliens - The native creatures of the alien world don''t like your factory. Build defenses and repel the attacks. The Factory Must Grow!', 35.00, 'https://cdn.wallpapersafari.com/26/74/HPOxYF.jpg', 'Wube Software', '2020-08-14', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (50, 'GTFO', 'Hardcore 4-player co-op horror FPS', 'GTFO is a hardcore 4 player cooperative horror FPS. You and your friends are prisoners forced to explore the vast underground complex while searching for important resources. Your survival depends on your ability to communicate, coordinate, and count your bullets. Work Together or Fail - GTFO is about tension and cooperation. Explore the Complex - Delve into the depths of The Complex. Some areas are just a walk in the park, others are guaranteed nightmares. Choose Your Approach - Every Rundown is unique, and every expedition poses new challenges. Discuss with your team, develop a plan, and execute it. The Warden - An Artificial Intelligence called The Warden controls the population and layout of The Complex. Every new expedition is unique. Rundowns - Each Rundown features 5 unique expeditions, each with specific objectives and unique challenges. Regular content updates keep the game fresh. Strategic Combat - Ammo and resources are scarce.', 39.99, 'https://cdn-ext.fanatical.com/production/product/1280x720/94ec4325-d666-4d7c-a8c4-17607ca3fb60.jpeg', '10 Chambers', '2021-12-09', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (51, 'Hollow Knight: Silksong', 'Play as Hornet in new kingdoms', 'Discover a haunting new kingdom, protect its people from deadly enemies and solve ancient mysteries as you ascend on a deadly pilgrimage to the kingdom''s peak! Hollow Knight: Silksong is the sequel to the award winning action-adventure. As the lethal hunter Hornet, journey to all-new lands, discover new powers, battle vast hordes of bugs and beasts and uncover ancient secrets tied to your nature and your past. Explore, Fight and Survive - Hunt down your foes and take on titanic bosses. Over 150 new enemies. Master an Arsenal of Deadly Skills - Acrobatic prowess, fleetness of foot and deadly needle arts. Craft powerful tools to aid you. A Lush, Hand-Drawn World - Descend into shimmering caverns and cross wind-blasted peaks to explore haunted workshops and grand gothic ruins. Exquisite Character Design - Meet a cast of all-new characters, some friendly, many not so much.', 29.99, 'https://static0.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/feature-images-53.png?&fit=crop&w=1600&h=900', 'Team Cherry', '2025-06-12', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (52, 'The Binding of Isaac: Repentance', 'Ultimate roguelike dungeon crawler with items', 'The ultimate edition of the genre-defining roguelike! The Binding of Isaac: Repentance is the ultimate version of Binding of Isaac, featuring all content from the Rebirth, Afterbirth and Afterbirth+ expansions, plus hundreds of new features and improvements. The ultimate edition of the genre-defining roguelike includes all content from Rebirth, Afterbirth, and Afterbirth+. 5000+ Room Layouts - A near-infinite amount of replayability awaits. 100+ New Enemies - Each with unique behaviors and attack patterns. 130+ New Items - Endless combinations of items create unique gameplay experiences. New Alternate Path - Make choices that drastically alter your run. Boss Rush and Daily Run Modes - Push your skills to the limit. Unlockables Everywhere - 637 achievements to hunt down. Co-op Mode - Local co-op with up to 4 players. Mod Support - Thousands of mods available through the workshop.', 19.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/134/1348087.jpeg', 'Nicalis', '2021-03-31', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (53, 'Pathfinder: Wrath of the Righteous', 'Epic CRPG battling demonic invasion', 'Embark on a journey to a realm overrun by demons in a new epic RPG from the creators of the critically acclaimed Pathfinder: Kingmaker. Explore the nature of good and evil, learn the true cost of power, and rise as a Mythic Hero capable of deeds beyond mortal expectations. Your path will lead you to the Worldwound, where the opening of a rift to the Abyss has unleashed all-consuming terror across the land. For over a century, the neighboring nations have fought fearlessly, trying to drive the enemy back — but to little avail. New Crusade - Lead your army and challenge demon lords. Conquer new regions as you find your place in the world of Golarion. Choose Your Mythic Path - Become an Angel, a Lich, an Aeon, a Demon or something else entirely. Your choice will determine the fate of everyone. Epic CRPG - Enjoy a classic RPG experience inspired by games like Baldur''s Gate. Meet companions with deep stories.', 49.99, 'https://images2.alphacoders.com/117/1171119.jpg', 'Owlcat Games', '2021-09-02', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (54, 'Pathfinder: Kingmaker', 'Classic isometric RPG with kingdom management', 'Pathfinder: Kingmaker is the first isometric party-based computer RPG set in the Pathfinder fantasy universe. Enjoy a classic RPG experience inspired by games like Baldur''s Gate, Fallout 1 and 2 and Arcanum. Explore and conquer the Stolen Lands and make them your kingdom! To establish a kingdom, explorers must first clear the Stolen Lands of any threats, both mundane and supernatural. Claim These Lands - Explore the Stolen Lands, a region that has been contested territory for centuries. Survive the Wilderness - The Stolen Lands are yours for the taking, but first survive. Hundreds of kingdom events, large and small, await your judgment. Your Kingdom - Expand your kingdom, opening up new territories and allowing you to build new towns and communities. Companions - Meet a diverse cast of companions. Pursue romance with your favorites. Classic RPG Gameplay - Core mechanics based on Pathfinder Tabletop rules.', 39.99, 'https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp9191940.jpg', 'Owlcat Games', '2018-09-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (55, 'The Elder Scrolls III: Morrowind', 'Epic fantasy RPG set in the volcanic province of Morrowind', 'The Elder Scrolls III: Morrowind is an epic, open-ended single-player game where you create and play any kind of character you can imagine. Be the noble hero embarking on an epic quest, or an insidious thief rising to leadership of his guild. Be a malevolent sorcerer developing the ultimate spell of destruction, or a reverent healer searching for the cure to a plague. Your actions define your character, and your gameplay changes and evolves in response to your actions. Confront the assassins'' guild, and they take out a contract on you. Impress them, and they try to recruit you instead. No two sagas are the same in the world of Morrowind. Epic Open-Ended RPG - Create any character and pursue any quest you desire. Vast Detailed World - Explore exotic locations from small villages to massive cities. Engaging Storyline - Follow the main plot or explore hundreds of side quests. Freedom to Play - Ultimate character customization and development.', 14.99, 'https://images8.alphacoders.com/404/404531.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2002-05-01', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (56, 'The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion', 'Open-world action RPG in the imperial province of Cyrodiil', 'After the mysterious and untimely death of the Emperor, desperate factions vie for control of Tamriel''s throne. With the Empire ready to crumble, the gates of Oblivion open and demons march upon the land – laying waste to everything in their path. To turn the tide of darkness, you must find the lost heir to the throne and unravel the sinister plot that threatens to destroy all of Tamriel. Live Another Life in Another World. Create and play any character you can imagine, from the noble warrior to the sinister assassin to the wizened sorcerer. An all-new combat and magic system brings first person role-playing to a new level of intensity where you feel every blow. Oblivion is a single-player game that takes place in Tamriel''s capital province, Cyrodiil. You are given the task of finding the hidden heir to a throne that sits empty, the previous emperor having been killed by an unknown assassin. With no true Emperor, the gates to Oblivion open, and demons begin to invade Cyrodiil and attack its people and towns. It''s up to you to find the lost heir to the throne and unravel the sinister plot that threatens to destroy all of Tamriel. A groundbreaking Radiant AI system gives Oblivion''s characters full 24/7 schedules.', 19.99, 'https://4kwallpapers.com/images/wallpapers/the-elder-scrolls-3840x2160-22190.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2006-03-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (57, 'The Elder Scrolls Online', 'Massively multiplayer RPG set in Tamriel', 'Experience an ever-expanding story across all of Tamriel in The Elder Scrolls Online, an award-winning online RPG. Explore a rich, living world with friends or embark upon a solo adventure. Enjoy complete control over how your character looks and plays, from the weapons you wield to the skills you learn – the choices you make will shape your destiny. Welcome to a world without limits. Go anywhere, do anything, and play your way in The Elder Scrolls Online. Battle, craft, steal, siege, or explore, and combine different types of equipment and abilities to create your own style of play. The choice is yours to make in a persistent, ever-growing Elder Scrolls world. Choose from hundreds of new weapons and abilities, and engage in challenging content with your friends or explore the far reaches of Tamriel as a lone adventurer. Join over 20 million players in the award-winning online multiplayer RPG. Explore dangerous caves and dungeons, embark on adventurous quests across Tamriel, and engage in challenging PvP battles. Player vs. Player – Battle for dominance across Cyrodiil. Become Emperor and command an Alliance to victory. Join a guild and take keeps and resources from enemy players.', 19.99, 'https://esossl-a.akamaihd.net/assets/img/cms/media/703c3682d0c436626bd38dfe4dd41b36_the-elder-scrolls-online-elsweyr_original.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2014-04-04', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (58, 'Fallout 3', 'Post-nuclear role-playing game in the Capital Wasteland', 'Vault 101 – Jewel of the Wastes. For 200 years, Vault 101 has faithfully served the surviving residents of Washington DC and its environs, now known as the Capital Wasteland. Though the global atomic war of 2077 left the US all but destroyed, the residents of Vault 101 enjoy a life free from the constant stress of the outside world. Giant radiated insects, raiders, hysteria and of course, the ever present threat of radiation are all problems for the outside world. As a resident of Vault 101, you are faced with the greatest crisis your home has ever known – your father has left. What could have made him leave? What dangers will you face in your search? When you leave Vault 101, you will explore vast radioactive wastes, gaining experience and leveling up your character. Along your journey you''ll experience action-packed combat, interact with interesting characters, and make important decisions that will affect the world around you. Vault-Tec engineers have constructed a revolutionary system from which to experience the world: The Pip-Boy 3000. Use the Pip-Boy 3000 to manage your inventory, access the map, tune into the radio stations, and much more. Create any kind of character you want.', 9.99, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTI4ZDQ4ZWMtYjRmNy00ZjBiLWEzYzQtYWEwNTM0YmU1MGZlXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_FMjpg_UX1000_.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2008-10-28', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (59, 'Fallout: New Vegas', 'Post-apocalyptic RPG set in the Mojave Wasteland', 'Welcome to Vegas. New Vegas. It''s the kind of town where you dig your own grave prior to being shot in the head and left for dead...and that''s before things really get ugly. It''s a town of dreamers and desperados being torn apart by warring factions vying for complete control of this desert oasis. It''s a place where the right kind of person with the right kind of weaponry can really make a name for themselves, and make more than an enemy or two along the way. As you battle your way across the heat-blasted Mojave Wasteland, the colossal Hoover Dam, and the neon drenched Vegas Strip, you''ll be introduced to a colorful cast of characters, power-hungry factions, special weapons, mutated creatures and much more. Choose sides in the upcoming war or declare "winner takes all" and crown yourself the King of New Vegas. Enjoy your stay! Feel the Heat in New Vegas! Not even nuclear fallout could slow the hustle of Sin City. Explore the treacherous wastes of the Great Southwest from the safety and comfort of your own vault. Make allies and enemies with various factions. Your actions will affect how different factions view you, opening up or closing off different quests and story paths.', 9.99, 'https://cubiccreativity.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/fallout-new-vegas-header.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2010-10-19', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (60, 'Fallout 4', 'Open-world action RPG in post-apocalyptic Boston', 'Bethesda Game Studios, the award-winning creators of Fallout 3 and The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim, welcome you to the world of Fallout 4 – their most ambitious game ever, and the next generation of open-world gaming. As the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a world destroyed by nuclear war. Every second is a fight for survival, and every choice is yours. Only you can rebuild and determine the fate of the Wasteland. Welcome home. Do whatever you want in a massive open world with hundreds of locations, characters, and quests. Join multiple factions vying for power or go it alone, the choices are all yours. An all-new next generation graphics and lighting engine brings to life the world of Fallout like never before. From the blasted forests of the Commonwealth to the ruins of Boston, every location is packed with dynamic detail. Violence and tragedy prep you for your lucky break. S.P.E.C.I.A.L. system allows you to develop your own playstyle. With the Wasteland Workshop, design and set cages to capture live creatures. Collect, customize, and improve over 50 base weapons with 700+ modifications. Battle your way through the war-torn ruins of post-apocalyptic Boston.', 19.99, 'https://techprincess.it/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Fallout-4-Anniversary-Edition_cropped.webp', 'Bethesda', '2015-11-10', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (61, 'Borderlands', 'Shoot-and-loot FPS with millions of guns', 'Discover the co-op shooter-looter that started it all, crammed with content and enhancements! Equip bazillions of guns as one of 4 trigger-happy mercenaries, each with unique RPG skills. Take on the lawless desolate planet Pandora in pursuit of powerful alien technology: The Vault. With new guns, visual upgrades, all 4 add-on packs and more, experience the highly acclaimed FPS/RPG solo or together with friends! Four player online cooperative gameplay. Bazillions of Guns: Rocket-launching shotguns, enemy-torching revolvers, SMGs that fire lightning rounds, and tons more. The revolutionary shooter-looter that started it all returns. Play as one of four new vault hunters facing off against a massive new world of creatures, psychos and the evil mastermind, Handsome Jack. Jump into the mayhem as a gunslinging Siren, a futuristic-minded Commando, a trigger-happy Gunzerker, or the silent but deadly Assassin. Travel the vast reaches of Pandora to stop Jack from awakening an ancient alien evil known only as "the Warrior". Collect rare treasures and unlock new skills in a massive world filled with explosions, loot and mayhem.', 19.99, 'https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp3508254.jpg', '2K Games', '2009-10-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (62, 'Borderlands 2', 'The sequel to the original shoot-and-loot FPS', 'A new era of shoot and loot is about to begin. Play as one of four new vault hunters facing off against a massive new world of creatures, psychos and the evil mastermind, Handsome Jack. Make new friends, arm them with a bazillion weapons and fight alongside them in 4 player co-op on a relentless quest for revenge and redemption across the undiscovered and unpredictable living planet. All-New Characters and All-New Classes: Four all new playable classes including the Siren, the Commando, the Gunzerker and the Assassin. Customize each character with their skill tree and grow in power. Dynamic Co-op: Share your adventures with friends online. Borderlands 2 features a seamless system enabling you to drop in and drop out of a campaign without ever having to restart the game. On top of that you can even take your new gear from any game to your own. World Connected Story: Find yourself left for dead in the frozen tundra of Pandora as you begin your quest of revenge and redemption. Expose the evil surrounding the Hyperion Corporation and take on the perpetrator of a universe-wide grand deception – the nefarious Hyperion CEO, Handsome Jack.', 19.99, 'https://img.goodfon.com/original/1920x1080/9/69/borderlands-2-the-psycho.jpg', '2K Games', '2012-09-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (63, 'Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel', 'The story between Borderlands and Borderlands 2', 'Launch into the Borderlands universe and shoot''n''loot your way through a brand new adventure that rockets you onto Pandora''s moon in Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel! Discover the story behind Borderlands 2 villain, Handsome Jack, and his rise to power. Taking place between the original Borderlands and Borderlands 2, the Pre-Sequel gives you a whole lotta new gameplay featuring the genre blending fusion of shooter and RPG gameplay that players can''t get enough of. Float through the air with each low gravity jump while taking enemies down from above using new ice and laser weapons. Catch-a-ride on the lunar landscape with new vehicles equipped with deadly weapons allowing for brand new vehicular combat. Fight alongside future megalomaniacal tyrant Handsome Jack, while meeting a mix of new and old friends in an adventure that will continue the story of Pandora and show you the methods behind Jack''s madness. Help put Handsome Jack on the throne and watch his transformation from hero to villain. Experience weaponized oxygen and deadly laser weapons. The moon''s low-gravity environment will increase your air time and allow for awesome new combat strategies.', 19.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/548/thumb-1920-548778.jpg', '2K Games', '2014-10-14', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (64, 'Borderlands 3', 'The original shooter-looter returns', 'The original shooter-looter returns, packing bazillions of guns and a mayhem-fueled adventure! Blast through new worlds and enemies as one of four new Vault Hunters. Play solo or with friends to take on insane enemies, score loads of loot and save your home from the most ruthless cult leaders in the galaxy. Stop the fanatical Calypso Twins from uniting the bandit clans and claiming the galaxy''s ultimate power. Only you, a thrill-seeking Vault Hunter, have the arsenal and allies to take them down. Become one of four extraordinary Vault Hunters, each with unique abilities, playstyles, deep skill trees, and tons of personalization options. All Vault Hunters are viable for solo and co-op play, so choose your favorite and get ready to save the galaxy. With bazillions of guns and gadgets, every fight is a surprise. Rocket launchers that spawn volcanoes, rifles that shoot-and-loot enemies, SMGs that laugh at your foes – we''ve got you covered. Discover new worlds beyond Pandora. From metropolitan cities to deadly swamps and everything in between. Borderlands 3 is bigger and better than ever. Play with your friends in seamless online co-op.', 59.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/100/1004495.jpg', '2K Games', '2019-09-13', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (65, 'Tiny Tinas Wonderlands', 'Fantasy spin-off of the Borderlands series', 'Embark on an epic adventure full of whimsy, wonder, and high-powered weaponry! Bullets, magic, and broadswords collide across this chaotic fantasy world brought to life by the unpredictable Tiny Tina. Roll your own multiclass hero and loot, shoot, slash, and cast your way through outlandish monsters and treasure-filled dungeons on a quest to stop the tyrannical Dragon Lord. Everyone''s welcome, so join the party, throw on your adventuring boots, and be Chaotic Great! Your Wonderlands Await! Bullets, magic, and broadswords collide across a chaotic fantasy world brought to life by the utterly unpredictable Tiny Tina. This epic tabletop adventure is full of whimsy, wonder, and high-powered weaponry. Roll your own multiclass hero and jump into the adventure – you can be whoever you want in the Wonderlands! Guns, Spells, and More! Wield a mighty arsenal of weaponry, from traditional shooters to devastating spells. Loot, shoot, and cast on a journey to thwart the tyrannical Dragon Lord. Dive into a world packed with diverse environments and a massive cast of characters in a branching story. Partner up with up to three friends to blast your way through.', 59.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/124/1249522.jpg', '2K Games', '2022-03-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (66, 'Pokemon Sword', 'Begin your adventure to become a Pokemon Champion', 'Begin your adventure as a Pokémon Trainer by choosing one of three new partner Pokémon: Grookey, Scorbunny, or Sobble. Then embark on a journey in the new Galar region, where you''ll challenge the troublemakers of Team Yell, while unraveling the mystery behind the Legendary Pokémon Zacian and Zamazenta! Explore the Wild Area, a vast expanse of land where the player can freely control the camera. Team up with three other players locally or online in the new Dynamax Adventures, in which you''ll explore Pokémon Dens and encounter Dynamax Pokémon! In these dens, you''ll find all sorts of powerful Pokémon, with new Pokémon that can Gigantamax appearing for the first time. New Pokémon from Galar like Grookey, Scorbunny and Sobble. Travel the Galar region and discover new Pokémon. Battle and catch Pokémon in the Wild Area. Become the champion of the Galar region. Dynamax your Pokémon into huge titans in battle. Explore Max Raid Battles where you''ll team up with other trainers. The adventure awaits in a new region filled with new Pokémon and exciting new characters.', 59.99, 'https://i.pinimg.com/736x/4c/1a/2f/4c1a2f82fe4596714475a0e82d383c41.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2019-11-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (67, 'Pokemon Shield', 'Discover the Galar region and catch new Pokemon', 'Begin your adventure as a Pokémon Trainer by choosing one of three new partner Pokémon: Grookey, Scorbunny, or Sobble. In Pokémon Shield, you''ll explore the Galar region with new Pokémon to catch and Gigantamax Pokémon battles to master. Join Trainers across the globe to discover Gigantamax Pokémon. Certain species of Pokémon can not only Dynamax but can also Gigantamax to become even larger and change their appearance—some even have exclusive G-Max moves to unleash. Team up with friends to catch all-new Pokémon in Max Raid Battles. In the Wild Area, team up with three other Trainers to take on a Dynamax Pokémon in Max Raid Battles! You can even team up with friends locally or online. In Max Raid Battles, you''ll face off against wild Dynamax Pokémon who are extra powerful. Explore the Galar region with unique Pokémon you''ll only find in Pokémon Shield. Some Pokémon, like the Fighting-type Sirfetch''d and the Ghost-type Cursola, only appear in Shield. Choose your starter Pokémon and begin your adventure in the idyllic countryside of the Galar region.', 59.99, 'https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.e97a5cfa486a3986e72bc0162d02188e?rik=I2knXUuFQ1X%2few&pid=ImgRaw&r=0', 'Nintendo', '2019-11-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (68, 'Pokemon Legends: Arceus', 'Action RPG set in the ancient Sinnoh region', 'Get ready for a new kind of grand, Pokémon adventure in Pokémon Legends: Arceus, a brand-new game from Game Freak that blends action and exploration with the RPG roots of the Pokémon series. Embark on survey missions in the ancient Hisui region. Aim and throw Poké Balls at wild Pokémon to catch them. Battle and catch Pokémon with a new action-oriented battle system. Your adventure takes place in the expansive natural majesty of the Hisui region, where you are tasked with studying Pokémon to complete the region''s first Pokédex. Mount Coronet rises from the center, surrounded on all sides by areas with distinct environments. In this era—long before the events of the Pokémon Brilliant Diamond and Pokémon Shining Pearl games—you can find newly discovered Pokémon like Wyrdeer, an evolution of Stantler, and new regional forms like Hisuian Growlithe! Along the way, uncover the mystery surrounding the special Pokémon known as Arceus. Action meets RPG as the Pokémon series reaches a new frontier. You can catch, survey, and research wild Pokémon in long-gone era of the Sinnoh region to create and complete the region''s first Pokédex.', 59.99, 'https://static0.gamerantimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/pokemon-legends-arceus-crimson-mirelands-featured-image-2.jpg?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop', 'Nintendo', '2022-01-28', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (69, 'Pokemon Scarlet', 'Explore the open world of the Paldea region', 'Begin your adventure in Pokémon Scarlet! Your journey begins when you choose one of three brand-new Pokémon—Sprigatito, Fuecoco, or Quaxly—and head out into the sprawling region of Paldea. A new generation of Pokémon. An  open world with no boundaries. Pokémon Scarlet lets you explore at your leisure and not in an order dictated by the story. You''ll join one of three story paths: find Titan Pokémon in the Path of Legends, or investigate Team Star as part of Starfall Street, or aim for the Champion Rank in Victory Road. Along your journey you''ll come across special Pokémon that are larger and more powerful than others of the same species—Titan Pokémon! You can also adventure with friends! Up to 4 players can adventure together! The lands of the Paldea region are filled with lakes, wastelands, and mountain ranges, creating a variety of different landscapes where numerous Pokémon species make their home. The region is bustling with various people making their livelihood in different ways. Travel with the legendary Pokémon Koraidon. Discover treasure in every corner of Paldea. Explore an open world where various towns blend seamlessly.', 59.99, 'https://www.nintendo.com/eu/media/images/10_share_images/games_15/nintendo_switch_4/2x1_NSwitch_PokemonScarletViolet_Scarlet_enGB_image1600w.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2022-11-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (70, 'Pokemon Violet', 'Discover new Pokemon in the Paldea region', 'Begin your adventure in Pokémon Violet! Choose from three new partner Pokémon and adventure in the Paldea region, where Pokémon have adapted to live alongside people in towns and across wild open spaces. You''ll be able to experience three different stories in this bold adventure! In the classic Victory Road story, you''ll encounter Gym Leaders and challenge the Pokémon League! In Path of Legends, you''ll meet special Pokémon known as Titan Pokémon! And in Starfall Street, you''ll battle against Team Star, a crew made up of school delinquents! Embark on an independent study called a Treasure Hunt! You''ll explore the sprawling Paldea region at your own pace as you work on an assignment to find your very own treasure. Travel across the vast open world with the legendary Pokémon Miraidon! You can also cooperate with your friends via the Union Circle! The lands of Paldea are home to a wide range of Pokémon, including Pokémon types you''ve never seen before! Some Pokémon change form when they Terastallize! You''ll take on the Gym Challenge against some of the toughest Trainers in Paldea.', 59.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRggdIdHULHPg0y-NV5NFg90Y_FBJ27sbXiUw&s', 'Nintendo', '2022-11-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (71, 'Super Mario Odyssey', 'Join Mario on a massive globe-trotting 3D adventure', 'Explore incredible places far from the Mushroom Kingdom as you join Mario and his new ally Cappy on a massive, globe-trotting 3D adventure. Use amazing new abilities—like the power to capture and control objects, animals, and enemies—to collect Power Moons so you can power up the Odyssey airship and save Princess Peach from Bowser''s wedding plans! Thanks to heroic, hat-shaped Cappy, Mario''s got new moves that''ll make you rethink his traditional run-and-jump gameplay—like cap jump, cap throw, and capture. Use captured cohorts such as enemies, objects, and animals to progress through the game and uncover loads of hidden collectibles. And if you feel like playing with a friend, just pass them a Joy-Con controller! Player 1 controls Mario while Player 2 controls Cappy. This team-up culminates in new and unexpected gameplay found only in Super Mario Odyssey. Explore huge 3D kingdoms filled with secrets and surprises. Collect Power Moons hidden throughout the game. Visit astonishing new locales and encounter familiar friends and foes.', 59.99, 'https://images2.alphacoders.com/854/854342.png', 'Nintendo', '2017-10-27', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (72, 'Super Mario Wonder', 'A new side-scrolling Mario adventure', 'The Super Mario Bros. franchise is making the jump to the Super Mario Bros. Wonder game for Nintendo Switch! Classic Mario side-scrolling gameplay is turned on its head with the addition of Wonder Flowers. These game-changing items trigger spectacular moments you have to see to believe. Witness pipes coming alive, wreak havoc as a giant spiky ball, and see even more unexpected events called Wonder Effects. Who knows what you''ll discover! You''ll also find Power-Ups including the Elephant Fruit. With this new power-up, Mario, Luigi, and friends can use their trunks to attack or interact with their environments. Choose from the largest cast of characters in a side-scrolling Mario game, including Mario, Luigi, Peach, Daisy, Yellow Toad, Blue Toad, and Toadette! You can also race through levels as Yoshi or Nabbit. Collect Wonder Seeds and flower coins as you adventure through the Flower Kingdom. Find hidden areas, fun secrets, and friendly characters. Experience classic side-scrolling action with a Wonder-ful twist! Collect Wonder Seeds and explore a mysterious land.', 59.99, 'https://images3.alphacoders.com/131/1319050.jpeg', 'Nintendo', '2023-10-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (73, 'The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom', 'The sequel to Breath of the Wild', 'An epic adventure awaits in the Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom game, only on the Nintendo Switch system. In this sequel to The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, you''ll decide your own path through the sprawling landscapes of Hyrule and the mysterious islands floating in the vast skies above. Can you harness the power of Link''s new abilities to fight back against the malevolent forces that threaten the kingdom? Explore the vast land—and skies—of Hyrule. An epic adventure awaits in the Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom game. The adventure is yours to create in a world fueled by your imagination. In this sequel to The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, you''ll decide your own path through the sprawling landscapes of Hyrule and the mysterious islands floating in the vast skies above. Can you harness the power of Link''s new abilities to fight back against the malevolent forces that threaten the kingdom? Use Link''s new abilities like Fuse and Ultrahand to create all-new ways to travel and fight. Fuse weapons to create countless combinations. Explore across the land, through the skies, and into the depths below. Create your own unique adventure.', 69.99, 'https://blog.richersounds.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Tears-of-the-Kingdom-wallpaper-1170x720-1.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2023-05-12', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (74, 'Metroid Dread', 'The newest 2D Metroid adventure', 'Join intergalactic bounty hunter Samus Aran in her first new 2D Metroid story in 19 years. Samus'' story continues after the events of Metroid Fusion when she descends upon planet ZDR to investigate a mysterious transmission sent to the Galactic Federation. The remote planet has been overrun by vicious alien lifeforms and chilling mechanical menaces. Samus is more agile and capable than ever, but can she overcome the inhuman threat stalking the depths of ZDR? Face off against unrelenting E.M.M.I. robots. Once DNA-extracting research machines, these E.M.M.I. are now hunting Samus. There''s no hope in fighting them, so run, hide, and stay out of sight. Feeling powerful yet? Take on a variety of creatures, each ready to stop Samus in her tracks. Acquire new and familiar abilities. Grapple, slide, shoot, and more as you explore. Power-ups help Samus survive, but also unlock new areas. Navigate an interconnected labyrinth. Explore the sprawling map, evade danger, and find secrets. Once you acquire abilities, backtrack to reach new areas. Intense atmosphere. Fully cel-shaded visuals bring a cold, inhospitable planet to life.', 59.99, 'https://metroid.nintendo.com/dread/assets/images/media/wallpapers/samus.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2021-10-08', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (75, 'Metroid Prime Remastered', 'The classic first-person adventure returns', 'Suit up for an iconic adventure. Intergalactic bounty hunter Samus Aran receives a distress signal from a wrecked frigate in orbit around planet Talon IV. Upon investigation, the frigate reveals itself to be a Space Pirate research facility. There, Samus encounters her nemesis, Meta Ridley, whom she pursues to the planet below. It''s up to her alone to explore the ancient ruins that sprawl beneath Talon IV''s surface, investigate a meteorite that crashed here long ago, and finally uncover the dark secret behind the Space Pirates'' insidious schemes. Discover the origins of the Prime saga in this masterfully remastered adventure. Explore Talon IV, a lush planet shrouded in mystery. Investigate the ancient ruins beneath its surface. Uncover the truth behind the Space Pirates'' dark schemes. Experience this legendary game like never before with updated graphics and immersive sound. Play with traditional controls or modern, dual-stick controls. Solve puzzles, fight enemies, and face off against massive bosses in first-person adventures. The first Metroid Prime game in over a decade. The adventure is just beginning. Suit up.', 39.99, 'https://i.redd.it/metroid-prime-remastered-4k-wallpapers-3840x2160-v0-hh0v6suu9lha1.png?width=3840&format=png&auto=webp&s=4fdce729588d8cd9eedcf9c578c8439956ff59bc', 'Nintendo', '2023-02-08', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (76, 'Splatoon 3', 'The ink-splatting multiplayer shooter returns', 'Enter the Splatlands, a sun-scorched desert inhabited by battle-hardened Inklings and Octolings. Splatsville, the city of chaos, is the adrenaline-fueled heart of this dusty wasteland. Even in this desolate environment, Turf War reigns supreme and battles rage in new stages located in the surrounding wilds. Dynamic new moves help these fighters dodge attacks and cover more ground, along with a new bow-shaped weapon to sling ink. Get ready to bring your splat skills to the next level! Jump into online and local multiplayer battles with new and returning modes. Compete in 4v4 Turf War battles online. Use dynamic new moves and a new bow-shaped weapon type. Discover Splatsville, the city of chaos. Join a colorful culture that''s really making waves! Story mode returns with a globe-trotting adventure. Join Agent 3 and allies in this tale of mystery and adventure. Explore the world and discover secrets. Try your hand at Salmon Run, a co-op mode where you and your teammates battle waves of dangerous Salmonid bosses. Take on new and returning bosses. Work together to splat them all. Become a fresh new Inkling or Octoling. Adventure awaits!', 59.99, 'https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ywHPzNdf1E0/hq720.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEhCK4FEIIDSFryq4qpAxMIARUAAAAAGAElAADIQj0AgKJD&rs=AOn4CLADSa_QVYGfktrsjDlftgg31zA6Qg', 'Nintendo', '2022-09-09', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (77, 'Animal Crossing: New Horizons', 'Build your island paradise', 'Escape to a deserted island and create your own paradise as you explore, create, and customize in Animal Crossing: New Horizons. Your island getaway has a wealth of natural resources that can be used to craft everything from tools to creature comforts. You can hunt down insects at the crack of dawn, decorate your paradise throughout the day, or enjoy sunset on the beach while fishing in the ocean. The time of day and season match real life, so each day on your island is a chance to check in and find new surprises all year round. Show off your island utopia to family and friends or pack your bags and visit theirs. Whether playing online or with others beside you, island living is even better when you can share it. Even without hopping on a plane, you''ll meet a cast of charming animal residents bursting with personality. Friendly faces like Tom Nook and Isabelle will lend their services and happily help you grow your budding community. Escape to your island getaway and customize your paradise! Make friends with adorable animal villagers and enjoy activities like fishing, fossil hunting, bug catching and more. Share your island paradise with others through local wireless play or online.', 59.99, 'https://static0.thegamerimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Animal-Crossing-New-Horizons-logo.jpg?w=1600&h=900&fit=crop', 'Nintendo', '2020-03-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (78, 'Mario Kart 8 Deluxe', 'The ultimate Mario Kart racing experience', 'Hit the road with the definitive version of Mario Kart 8 and play anytime, anywhere! Race your friends or battle them in a revised battle mode on new and returning battle courses. Play locally in up to 4-player multiplayer in 1080p while playing in TV Mode. Every track from the Wii U version, including DLC, makes a glorious return. Plus, the Inklings appear as all-new guest characters, along with returning favorites, such as King Boo, Dry Bones, and Bowser Jr.! Race through new courses and new battle modes. Race with up to 12 players locally or online in a variety of game modes including Grand Prix, VS Race, and Battle Mode. Smart Steering is available to help you stay on track. Anti-gravity allows you to drive on walls and upside down. Boost your way to the finish line. Customize your ride with a variety of kart bodies, wheels, and gliders. Grab a Joy-Con controller and race against family and friends. Up to 8 players can race simultaneously on Nintendo Switch. Racing has never been this exhilarating! Mario Kart 8 Deluxe includes all DLC and features from the Wii U version.', 59.99, 'https://i.pinimg.com/736x/71/43/9e/71439e0446c1728cd1ef20895e8005e3.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2017-04-28', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (79, 'Super Smash Bros. Ultimate', 'The ultimate fighting game crossover', 'Gaming icons clash in the ultimate brawl you can play anytime, anywhere! Smash rivals off the stage as new characters Simon Belmont and King K. Rool join Inkling, Ridley, and every fighter in Super Smash Bros. history. Enjoy enhanced speed and combat at new stages based on the Castlevania series, Super Mario Odyssey, and more! Having trouble choosing a stage? Then select the Stage Morph option to transform one stage into another while battling—a series first! Plus, new echo fighters Dark Samus, Richter Belmont, and Chrom join the battle. Whether you play locally or online, savor the faster combat, new attacks, and new defensive options, like a perfect shield. Every fighter is back! All past stages return, too! Over 100 stages in all! 74 fighters in the base game. 11 additional fighters available as DLC. Settle it in Smash! Fast combat, new items, new attacks and defensive options. Play anytime, anywhere! Stage Morph: Select two stages for battle, then watch them transform mid-battle. New fighters, stages, and game modes. Battle online or with friends.', 59.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcShSVkAEapiu0pLPGj3xjYKqdSPp07LSr4tXQ&s', 'Nintendo', '2018-12-07', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (80, 'Kirby and the Forgotten Land', 'Kirbys first fully 3D platforming adventure', 'Join Kirby in an unforgettable journey through a mysterious world in a delightful 3D platforming adventure. Take control of the powerful pink puffball, Kirby, and move around freely in 3D stages as you discover a mysterious world with abandoned structures from a past civilization. Copy enemies'' abilities like Sword and Ice and use them to attack and explore your surroundings! What journey awaits Kirby? Take a deep breath and get ready for an unforgettable adventure! Float off on an all-new adventure as the powerful pink puffball, Kirby. Explore in 3D stages as you discover a mysterious world. What has brought Kirby to this mysterious place? And who is the mysterious beast that attacks him? Join Kirby on a journey of discovery through a post-apocalyptic world. Use Mouthful Mode to gain unique powers by inhaling large objects. Transform into a car, a vending machine, and more. Work together with a friend in co-op play. Player 2 can control Bandana Waddle Dee! Float and fight along with a friend in the new co-op play mode. Adventure through a mysterious and forgotten land!', 59.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSVjOzTYCtW2GU_EvAKY68OF5uinDQ1ejuIGg&s', 'Nintendo', '2022-03-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (81, 'Fire Emblem: Three Houses', 'Tactical RPG with deep strategic combat', 'Fire Emblem: Three Houses is a landmark entry in the Fire Emblem series that masterfully blends tactical combat with deep character relationships and an epic, branching narrative. Set in the land of Fódlan, you play as a professor at the Garrigos Officers Academy, where you must choose to lead one of three noble houses—the Black Eagles, Blue Lions, or Golden Deer—each with their own unique students, perspectives, and storylines. The game is divided between calendar-based academy life, where you build relationships with students, train their skills, and explore the monastery, and intense grid-based tactical battles where positioning, weapon advantages, and character abilities determine victory or defeat. The Divine Pulse mechanic allows you to rewind turns, making the challenging combat more accessible without sacrificing strategic depth. Your choices significantly impact the story, leading to dramatically different routes and endings. With memorable characters, stunning anime-style cutscenes, a phenomenal soundtrack, and hundreds of hours of content across multiple playthroughs, Three Houses is essential for strategy RPG fans.', 59.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/game-screen-of-fire-emblem-three-houses-5xhajiq4obaozvtu.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2019-07-26', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (82, 'Xenoblade Chronicles 3', 'Epic JRPG with vast open environments', 'Xenoblade Chronicles 3 delivers a breathtaking JRPG experience with one of the most ambitious and emotionally resonant stories in the genre. Set in the war-torn world of Aionios, where two nations—Keves and Agnus—are locked in endless conflict, you control Noah and Mio, soldiers from opposing sides who discover a greater conspiracy that threatens their entire existence. The game features a massive open world filled with towering creatures, hidden secrets, and stunning vistas that reward exploration. Combat is a deep real-time system where you control a party of seven characters, each with unique roles, Arts, and abilities that can be chained together for devastating combos. The innovative Interlink system allows characters to fuse into powerful Ouroboros forms, adding another strategic layer. The story tackles profound themes of life, death, legacy, and the futility of war, with a cast of unforgettable characters whose relationships evolve beautifully throughout the 80+ hour journey. With a phenomenal soundtrack by Yasunori Mitsuda, gorgeous cel-shaded graphics, and an expansion that adds even more depth, Xenoblade Chronicles 3 stands as one of the Nintendo Switch''s finest RPGs.', 59.99, 'https://images.steamusercontent.com/ugc/1905603371525441982/793A90D0F6315F52F39AA3485AE1E8963D1C1137/?imw=637&imh=358&ima=fit&impolicy=Letterbox&imcolor=%23000000&letterbox=true', 'Nintendo', '2022-07-29', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (83, 'Luigi''s Mansion 3', 'Ghost-hunting adventure with Luigi', 'Luigi''s Mansion 3 is a charming and cleverly designed adventure that proves Luigi is more than capable of carrying his own franchise. When Luigi, Mario, Princess Peach, and friends are invited to a luxury hotel, they quickly discover it''s a trap set by the mischievous King Boo. Luigi must explore the haunted Last Resort hotel, a towering structure with themed floors ranging from medieval castles to ancient Egyptian tombs to film production studios, each with unique puzzles and ghost encounters. Armed with the upgraded Poltergust G-00 vacuum, Luigi can slam ghosts, blow them away, use a plunger for environmental puzzles, and even summon Gooigi—a gooey doppelganger who can squeeze through tight spaces and walk on spikes. The game brilliantly balances light puzzle-solving, exploration, and ghost-catching combat, with satisfying boss battles against uniquely designed ghosts. The detailed, expressive animations bring Luigi''s scaredy-cat personality to life, and the game is filled with environmental storytelling and hidden collectibles. Co-op play allows a second player to control Gooigi, and the separate ScareScraper mode offers randomized tower-climbing challenges for up to eight players online.', 59.99, 'https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/ar_16:9,c_lpad,w_1240/b_white/f_auto/q_auto/store/software/switch/70010000001620/2b166fb3197dacfde1d939acd6a976b9fbe3b1a32c54f9f0d2c8d23efb22412d', 'Nintendo', '2019-10-31', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (84, 'Pikmin 4', 'Command an army of plant-like Pikmin', 'Pikmin 4 is the most refined and accessible entry in Nintendo''s beloved strategy series, offering both newcomers and veterans a delightful adventure filled with charm and challenge. After a space explorer crashes on a mysterious planet, you must command an army of adorable plant-like creatures called Pikmin to explore a world from a miniature perspective, where everyday objects like bottles and toys become massive obstacles and treasures. The game introduces Oatchi, an incredibly helpful space dog who can carry Pikmin, break down walls, and even be ridden like a mount, fundamentally changing the flow of exploration and combat. With seven types of Pikmin—each with unique abilities like fire resistance, electrical conductivity, or super strength—strategic thinking is essential as you battle creatures, solve environmental puzzles, and recover treasure to fuel your ship. The new Dandori Battles add competitive time-trial challenges, while night expeditions introduce tower defense mechanics where you must protect Onions from nocturnal predators. With a more forgiving rewind feature, extensive customization for your character and Oatchi, and gorgeous graphics that bring the miniature world to life, Pikmin 4 is the definitive Pikmin experience.', 59.99, 'https://i.redd.it/w2h15orw2dja1.png', 'Nintendo', '2023-07-21', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (85, 'Bayonetta 3', 'Stylish action game from PlatinumGames', 'Bayonetta 3 continues PlatinumGames'' signature brand of over-the-top, stylish action with the Umbra Witch''s most ambitious adventure yet. This time, Bayonetta faces the Homunculi, artificial bioweapons threatening the multiverse itself, leading to reality-hopping battles across alternate dimensions and versions of familiar locations. The combat system retains the series'' satisfying flow of dodging at the last second to trigger Witch Time, unleashing devastating combos, and summoning massive demons with Torture Attacks, but adds the new Demon Masquerade ability, allowing Bayonetta to fuse with her Infernal Demon summons and gain new movement and attack options. You can even directly control titanic demons in kaiju-scale battles that demolish entire cityscapes. The game introduces playable alternate Bayonettas, including the sassy Viola, a witch-in-training with a completely different combat style centered around parrying. With spectacularly choreographed set pieces, an insane story that gleefully embraces camp and spectacle, unlockable costumes and weapons, and the series'' trademark jazzy soundtrack, Bayonetta 3 is an exhilarating, if polarizing, conclusion to the trilogy.', 59.99, 'https://cdn.mobygames.com/covers/11051237-bayonetta-3-nintendo-switch-front-cover.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2022-10-28', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (86, 'Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity', 'Hack-and-slash set 100 years before BOTW', 'Hyrule Warriors: Age of Calamity is a musou-style action game that serves as a prequel to The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild, exploring the catastrophic events 100 years before Link''s awakening. Developed by Omega Force and Nintendo, the game lets you experience the Great Calamity firsthand as you play Link, Zelda, Impa, and the four Champions—Daruk, Mipha, Revali, and Urbosa—each with distinct combat styles inspired by their abilities from BOTW. Mow down massive hordes of enemies across iconic Hyrulean locations, complete mission objectives, capture outposts, and face off against powerful bosses including Guardians, Lynels, and Calamity Ganon''s Blights. The game incorporates BOTW mechanics like the Sheikah Slate runes (bombs, Stasis, Magnesis, Cryonis), weapon durability, cooking, and even the physics-based interactions that made BOTW special. Unlock and upgrade characters, weapons, and abilities through an extensive progression system with hundreds of quests and challenges. Local two-player co-op allows friends to join the battle, and the story, while taking some creative liberties with the timeline, offers fan service and emotional moments for those invested in BOTW''s lore.', 59.99, 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81kLcRuqotL._AC_UF1000,1000_QL80_.jpg', 'Nintendo', '2020-11-20', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (87, 'Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze', 'Challenging 2D platformer', 'Donkey Kong Country: Tropical Freeze is widely regarded as one of the finest 2D platformers ever made, delivering pixel-perfect precision, creative level design, and punishing-but-fair difficulty. When the Snowmads, an invasion force of arctic animals, freeze Donkey Kong Island, DK and his friends must travel through six stunning islands to reclaim their home. Every level is a masterclass in design, with dynamic camera angles, rhythm-based platforming sequences, and environmental storytelling. Retro Studios'' attention to detail is phenomenal—from lush jungle canopies to underwater ruins to African savanna-inspired landscapes—every world feels distinct and alive. The soundtrack, composed by David Wise, is legendary, perfectly complementing the action with atmospheric and energetic tracks. Donkey Kong can roll, pound, and climb, while partners Diddy Kong (jetpack hover), Dixie Kong (helicopter spin), Cranky Kong (cane bounce), and newcomer Funky Kong (surfboard and extra health in Switch version) add unique abilities and strategies. With challenging bonus levels, hidden collectibles, time trial modes, and two-player co-op, Tropical Freeze offers substantial content for both casual players and hardcore speedrunners.', 59.99, 'https://purenintendo.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Donkey-Kong-Country-Tropical-Freeze-01.png', 'Nintendo', '2018-05-04', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (88, 'DOOM (2016)', 'Hell on Mars returns with brutal combat', 'DOOM (2016) is a triumphant reinvention of the classic FPS franchise, stripping away modern shooter conventions and returning to pure, adrenaline-fueled demon-slaying action. When a UAC facility on Mars accidentally opens a portal to Hell, you are the Doom Slayer, an unstoppable force of rage and destruction, armed with an arsenal of satisfying weapons from the iconic super shotgun to the devastating BFG 9000. The game encourages aggressive, in-your-face combat through its glory kill system—when enemies are staggered, you can perform brutal melee finishers that drop health, rewarding players for staying in the thick of battle rather than hiding behind cover. The campaign features intense arena encounters where waves of demons spawn in hellish Mars facilities and literal Hell dimensions, complemented by light platforming and exploration for secrets, upgrades, and lore collectibles. id Software''s id Tech 6 engine delivers smooth 60fps gunplay with incredibly detailed gore and environmental destruction. Mick Gordon''s industrial metal soundtrack dynamically intensifies during combat, becoming one of gaming''s most iconic scores. SnapMap mode allows custom level creation, while multiplayer offers classic modes, though the campaign''s relentless pace and perfect execution steal the show.', 19.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSrC4agnNSSJcQKcZzAtYgVVEB3MjCSiTM8_A&s', 'Bethesda', '2016-05-13', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (89, 'Prey (2017)', 'Sci-fi thriller aboard a space station', 'Prey is a deeply atmospheric sci-fi immersive sim from Arkane Studios that channels the spirit of System Shock while forging its own identity. Set aboard Talos I, a space station orbiting the moon in an alternate 2032, you wake as Morgan Yu to discover the station has been overrun by the Typhon, a hostile alien species capable of mimicking everyday objects. Armed with a wrench, firearms, and the revolutionary GLOO Cannon that creates climbable foam, you must explore the interconnected space station, uncovering the truth about your identity, the Typhon outbreak, and the morally ambiguous experiments conducted aboard. The game''s defining feature is the Neuromod system, which allows you to install alien and human abilities—everything from telekinesis and shapeshifting into objects (yes, you can become a coffee mug) to hacking and enhanced combat skills. The open-ended design encourages creative problem-solving; objectives can be completed through combat, stealth, hacking, environmental manipulation, or using alien powers. The station feels alive with environmental storytelling through emails, audio logs, and the tragic fates of crew members. Multiple endings reflect your moral choices, particularly whether you remain human or embrace alien power, making Prey a thinking player''s shooter with meaningful consequences.', 29.99, 'https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp4415849.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2017-05-05', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (90, 'Dishonored 2', 'Supernatural stealth action game', 'Dishonored 2 perfects Arkane Studios'' formula for emergent stealth-action gameplay, offering two distinct playable characters and some of the most imaginative level design in gaming history. Set 15 years after the original, you choose to play as either the royal protector Corvo Attano or the now-grown Empress Emily Kaldwin, each with unique supernatural abilities granted by the mysterious Outsider. Emily can Domino-link enemies so one''s fate affects others, pull enemies with Far Reach, create a shadowy doppelganger, and turn into a creeping cloud. Corvo returns with upgraded versions of his original powers like Blink teleportation, time manipulation, possession, and summoning rat swarms. The game''s genius lies in its open-ended missions where every objective can be completed through ghostly stealth, brutal combat, creative ability combinations, or clever environmental manipulation. Standout missions include the Clockwork Mansion with its reconfigurable rooms, A Crack in the Slab where you travel between timelines, and the non-lethal elimination options that require genuine thought. The Chaos system returns, where your violence (or mercy) affects the world state and ending. Enhanced graphics powered by the Void Engine bring the plague-ravaged Empire of the Isles to stunning life.', 39.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/dishonored-2-emily-corvo-throne-and-title-l5fqn651qgdb7vn4.jpg', 'Bethesda', '2016-11-11', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (91, 'The Outer Worlds', 'Sci-fi RPG from Obsidian Entertainment', 'The Outer Worlds is Obsidian Entertainment''s satirical take on corporate-controlled space colonization, delivering their trademark witty writing and choice-driven RPG mechanics in a colorful sci-fi setting. Set in the Halcyon colony at the edge of the galaxy, you awaken from cryosleep aboard a lost colonist ship and quickly become entangled in a conspiracy involving mega-corporations that control every aspect of life. The game features Obsidian''s signature dialogue system where your skills, attributes, and previous choices open different conversation paths, allowing you to talk, sneak, or shoot your way through quests. Recruit a diverse crew of companions, each with personal quests and strong opinions about your decisions. The Tactical Time Dilation system slows time during combat, letting you target specific body parts for strategic advantages. Explore alien worlds from the corporate town of Edgewater to the pleasure colony of Byzantium, each location dripping with dark humor about capitalism run amok. With multiple endings determined by your choices and faction allegiances, extensive character customization through skills and perks, and Obsidian''s trademark branching narratives, The Outer Worlds delivers a compact but densely packed RPG experience.', 39.99, 'https://xboxwire.thesourcemediaassets.com/sites/2/2023/03/TOWSCE_Microsoft_HeroTitle_1920x1080-3344ea0a8d15c2cd5bcc.jpg', 'Private Division', '2019-10-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (92, 'Bioshock Remastered', 'The classic immersive shooter remastered', 'BioShock Remastered brings the groundbreaking 2007 masterpiece to modern platforms with enhanced graphics, improved performance, and all DLC content. Descend into Rapture, an underwater utopia built in the 1940s by industrialist Andrew Ryan, now a nightmarish dystopia overrun by genetically modified citizens driven insane by ADAM, a substance that grants superhuman abilities. As Jack, the sole survivor of a plane crash, you navigate the art deco corridors of this sunken city, piecing together its tragic fall through audio diaries and environmental storytelling. Combat blends traditional firearms with Plasmids—genetic modifications that let you shoot lightning, incinerate enemies, control minds, or telekinetically hurl objects. The game encourages experimentation, rewarding creative combinations like electrifying water to shock nearby enemies or freezing foes before shattering them. Moral choices around harvesting or rescuing Little Sisters—young girls who gather ADAM—affect the story''s outcome. With its philosophical themes exploring Objectivism, free will, and the dangers of unchecked ambition, BioShock remains one of gaming''s most thought-provoking narratives. The remaster preserves everything that made the original special while making it accessible to new players.', 19.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS_TCwtS3WhWTxxqxi3B70YyWYSUJin28oLzw&s', '2K Games', '2016-09-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (93, 'Bioshock Infinite', 'Airborne city adventure', 'BioShock Infinite takes the series to new heights—literally—with a mind-bending adventure set in Columbia, a floating city suspended in the clouds above America in 1912. You play as Booker DeWitt, a former Pinkerton agent sent to Columbia to rescue Elizabeth, a young woman imprisoned in a tower since childhood. Elizabeth possesses the ability to open tears in space-time, creating portals to alternate realities, which factors heavily into both gameplay and the story''s reality-bending narrative. Columbia presents a stark contrast to Rapture: where the first game was dark and claustrophobic, Infinite is bright and open, though no less disturbing with its themes of American exceptionalism, religious extremism, and racial prejudice. Combat evolves with the Sky-Line system, magnetic rails that let you zoom around battlefields while raining death from above. Vigors replace Plasmids, offering similar supernatural abilities. The game builds to one of gaming''s most discussed and debated endings, exploring parallel universes, quantum mechanics, and the consequences of choice. With its stunning art direction, Garry Schyman''s soaring score, and the heartfelt relationship between Booker and Elizabeth, Infinite is an unforgettable journey.', 29.99, 'https://cdn.wallpapersafari.com/49/62/MacDUB.jpg', '2K Games', '2013-03-26', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (94, 'Metro Exodus', 'Post-apocalyptic first-person shooter', 'Metro Exodus is 4A Games'' ambitious evolution of the Metro series, trading the claustrophobic tunnels of Moscow''s metro for a sprawling, post-apocalyptic Russian wilderness. Set two years after Metro: Last Light, Artyom and a band of Spartan Rangers escape the metro aboard the Aurora, a steam locomotive, searching for a new life beyond the irradiated ruins. The game features large, open sandbox levels across diverse seasons—from the frozen Volga wasteland to the sun-scorched Caspian desert to the autumnal forests of Taiga—each offering multiple approaches to objectives, optional side content, and moral choices that affect the story. Survival mechanics remain tense: weapons must be cleaned and maintained, gas masks need filters in irradiated zones, and resources are scarce. The atmosphere is thick with dread as you battle mutated creatures, hostile human factions, and the harsh environment itself. Stealth and combat feel weighty and tactical, enhanced by a day-night cycle and dynamic weather. Your relationships with crew members aboard the Aurora evolve based on your actions, and the game features multiple endings determined by your choices. With ray-tracing support and incredible attention to detail, Metro Exodus is a haunting journey through a beautiful but deadly world.', 39.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTG7P9r4rzIDnTHUW6tnf0iKYih1GEXpkX1Mw&s', 'Deep Silver', '2019-02-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (95, 'Resident Evil 2 Remake', 'Survival horror classic reimagined', 'Resident Evil 2 Remake is a masterful reimagining of the 1998 survival horror classic, rebuilt from the ground up for modern audiences. Set during the Raccoon City zombie outbreak, you alternate between rookie cop Leon and student Claire as they navigate the overrun police station. Resources are scarce—every bullet counts—forcing careful inventory management. The relentless Mr. X creates unforgettable tension as his heavy footsteps echo closer. Multiple campaigns offer different perspectives, while unlockables encourage replayability.', 39.99, 'https://gameranx.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Resident-Evil-2-Remake-1080P-Wallpaper-1.jpg', 'Capcom', '2019-01-25', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (96, 'Resident Evil 3 Remake', 'Jill Valentine returns to Raccoon City', 'Resident Evil 3 Remake reimagines Jill Valentine''s desperate escape from Raccoon City. Playing as S.T.A.R.S. veteran Jill, you navigate zombie-infested streets while hunted by Nemesis, an intelligent bio-weapon. Unlike Mr. X, Nemesis is faster, more aggressive, and wields weapons, creating intense chases. The game is more action-oriented with dodge mechanics and emphasis on combat. Carlos Oliveira is playable in segments providing different perspectives. While shorter and more linear than RE2, RE3 compensates with relentless pacing and spectacular set pieces.', 39.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/featured/resident-evil-3-remake-7ne0hxnbalkvtj4i.jpg', 'Capcom', '2020-04-03', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (97, 'Devil May Cry 5', 'Stylish action returns to the legendary series', 'Devil May Cry 5 marks the triumphant return of Capcom''s legendary stylish action series. Three demon hunters—Nero with Devil Breaker arms, legendary Dante with expanded arsenal, and mysterious V commanding demonic familiars—must stop demon king Urizen. Each character plays completely differently. Combat rewards creativity, timing, and aggression with iconic style ranking from Dismal to SSS. The RE Engine delivers photorealistic graphics with fluid 60fps gameplay. The soundtrack dynamically layers as your style rank increases. DMC5 is the definitive stylish action experience.', 29.99, 'https://images6.alphacoders.com/926/926723.jpg', 'Capcom', '2019-03-08', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (98, 'NieR: Automata', 'Action RPG set in a post-apocalyptic world', 'NieR: Automata is an emotionally devastating philosophical action RPG where androids fight an endless proxy war against machines on post-apocalyptic Earth. You control 2B and 9S, battling through ruins of civilization. The game blends PlatinumGames'' fast action with bullet-hell segments, shifting from 3D to 2D to top-down perspectives. Its genius lies in multiple playthroughs that recontextualize everything, building to one of gaming''s most profound conclusions. Themes of consciousness, existentialism, and what it means to be alive permeate every aspect, elevated by a hauntingly beautiful soundtrack.', 39.99, 'https://i.pinimg.com/736x/43/12/45/4312458f66a7d1b48d4e2204d6d5efce.jpg', 'Square Enix', '2017-02-23', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (99, 'Persona 5 Royal', 'Enhanced version of the acclaimed JRPG', 'Persona 5 Royal is the definitive version of Atlus''s acclaimed JRPG. You play Joker, a framed student who discovers the Metaverse—a realm born from humanity''s twisted desires. By day, attend school and build relationships. By night, become a Phantom Thief, infiltrating Palaces to reform society. The game brilliantly balances life simulation with dungeon crawling. Turn-based combat exploits enemy weaknesses for extra actions, while negotiating recruits Personas. Royal adds new semester, party member Kasumi, expanded arcs, and quality-of-life improvements. With stylish presentation, jazz-funk soundtrack, social commentary, and 100+ hours, Persona 5 Royal is JRPG perfection.', 59.99, 'https://i.redd.it/dajomsl5wqw91.jpg', 'Atlus', '2022-10-21', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (100, 'Final Fantasy VII Remake Intergrade', 'Reimagining of the iconic RPG', 'Final Fantasy VII Remake Intergrade is Square Enix''s ambitious reimagining of the first portion of the 1997 classic, expanding Midgar into a full game. Control Cloud Strife fighting Shinra Electric Power Company. Combat blends real-time action with tactical menu commands, letting you control any party member and unleash special abilities. Intergrade includes PS5 enhancements, Yuffie DLC featuring ninja infiltration story, enhanced visuals and faster loads. The soundtrack reimagines iconic themes. Character development is exceptional, particularly between Cloud, Tifa, Aerith, and Barret. It modernizes a legendary game while charting its own path.', 69.99, 'https://fyre.cdn.sewest.net/ffvii-hub/67f44d1bf51210ac4358eb9d/ffvii-intergrade-16x9-2721107475932488.jpg', 'Square Enix', '2021-06-10', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (101, 'Dragon Age: Inquisition', 'Epic fantasy RPG from BioWare', 'Dragon Age: Inquisition is BioWare''s triumphant fantasy epic in Thedas. When an explosion tears open the Veil, you lead the Inquisition to restore order. Character creation affects dialogue and story branches. Explore massive regions from Hinterlands to Emerald Graves, filled with quests and strategic strongholds. Tactical camera enables pause-and-play strategy. Build your Inquisition through War Table choices, recruit agents, gain influence. Romance characters like Cassandra, Iron Bull, Dorian, Solas with deep personal quests. Trespasser DLC provides essential closure. Hundreds of hours of content, memorable characters, political intrigue, and lasting choices earned Game of the Year.', 19.99, 'https://images5.alphacoders.com/556/thumb-1920-556193.jpg', 'EA', '2014-11-18', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (102, 'Mass Effect Legendary Edition', 'The complete Mass Effect trilogy remastered', 'Mass Effect Legendary Edition is the definitive way to experience BioWare''s space opera trilogy. Follow Commander Shepard''s journey from discovering Reaper threat to uniting the galaxy. One of gaming''s most ambitious narratives where choices carry across all three games, affecting relationships, species'' survival, and galaxy''s fate. ME1 receives significant combat improvements. Romance spans entire trilogy. ME1 emphasizes exploration, ME2 focuses on character-driven suicide mission prep, ME3 delivers emotional conclusion. Legendary Edition includes enhanced textures, better framerates, unified character creator, and refined gameplay across all three games.', 59.99, 'https://www.psu.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DragonAge-Inquisition-PS4-Wallpapers-18.jpg', 'EA', '2021-05-14', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (103, 'Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order', 'Action-adventure set in the Star Wars universe', 'Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order is Respawn''s exceptional single-player adventure five years after Revenge of the Sith. Play Cal Kestis, former Padawan hiding Force abilities until discovered by Empire. Galaxy-spanning journey to rebuild Jedi Order while hunted by Inquisitors and Darth Vader. Combat inspired by Dark Souls emphasizing parrying and enemy patterns with forgiving difficulty options. Unlock Force powers like Push, Pull, Slow integrating into combat and puzzles. Explore interconnected alien worlds gaining abilities that open new areas in Metroidvania fashion. BD-1 droid provides adorable companionship. Respectful lore, spectacular lightsaber combat, memorable characters, and perfect canon fit.', 39.99, 'https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1172380/capsule_616x353.jpg?t=1748950986', 'EA', '2019-11-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (104, 'It Takes Two', 'Co-op action adventure', 'It Takes Two is Hazelight Studios'' Game of the Year 2021 co-op masterpiece requiring two players. Married couple Cody and May transform into dolls, forcing cooperation through fantastical journey. Every chapter introduces entirely new mechanics from shooting to platforming to flying to rhythm games, all for asymmetric cooperation. One manipulates time while other navigates, constantly surprising with variety. Story tackles real relationship issues with humor and heart. Jaw-dropping visual variety, creative bosses, optional mini-games. Josef Fares'' cinematic direction redefines co-op gaming. Friend''s Pass lets one owner invite friend free.', 39.99, 'https://i.pinimg.com/originals/0f/53/74/0f5374155b8d2f21316fe9ad8e5163ab.jpg', 'EA', '2021-03-26', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (105, 'A Way Out', 'Co-op only narrative adventure', 'A Way Out is Hazelight''s narrative co-op experience requiring two players, following prisoners Leo and Vincent breaking out and going on the run. Designed exclusively for co-op with split-screen throughout. Friend''s Pass means only one person needs to own it. Uses cooperation to tell cinematic story with players experiencing different perspectives simultaneously. Gameplay varies from stealth to driving to emotional conversations. Split-screen dynamically adapts. Story builds to gut-wrenching twist affecting entire journey. Motion-captured performances, 70s soundtrack. Josef Fares'' commitment to meaningful cooperative narrative shows games can tell stories impossible in other mediums. Best played in one sitting with close friend.', 29.99, 'https://cdn1.epicgames.com/spt-assets/a037fc78ee9d47b98466f17b44c46288/a-way-out-y92bk.jpg?resize=1&w=480&h=270&quality=medium', 'EA', '2018-03-23', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (106, 'Escape from Tarkov', 'Hardcore realistic online first-person action RPG/Simulator with MMO features', 'Escape from Tarkov is Battlestate Games'' uncompromising hardcore tactical FPS blending survival, RPG progression, and extraction gameplay. Set in sealed-off Russian city, play PMC or Scav surviving and escaping with loot while fighting players, AI, and managing realistic survival mechanics. Every raid is high-stakes: bring gear and extract within time limit, but death means losing everything. Realistic weapon handling with hundreds of guns, intricate medical systems where different body parts take specific damage, stamina management, player-driven economy. Hideout allows crafting between raids. Learning maps takes dozens of hours. Exceptional sound design makes every firefight terrifying. Steep learning curve punishes mistakes brutally but offers unmatched tension and satisfaction.', 44.99, 'https://wallpapers.com/images/featured/escape-from-tarkov-8ov2fwmmir49ncsl.jpg', 'Battlestate Games', '2017-07-27', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (107, 'Arc Raiders', 'Cooperative third-person shooter with extraction mechanics', 'Arc Raiders is Embark Studios'' upcoming cooperative extraction shooter set in retro-futuristic alternate Earth facing robotic invaders called ARC. Built in Unreal Engine 5, play as Raider venturing into dangerous zones gathering resources and extracting before time runs out. Emphasizes teamwork with squads up to three players scavenging technology and surviving mechanical threats from small drones to towering bosses. Dynamic weather and day-night cycles affect gameplay. Extraction mechanics create tension—stay longer for better loot but risk losing everything. Retro-futuristic aesthetic blends 80s nostalgia with post-apocalyptic sci-fi. Founded by former Battlefield developers. Persistent progression improves equipment for future raids. Focuses on emergent gameplay and cooperative strategy.', 39.99, 'https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FGgK2piXMAg6yDp.jpg', 'Embark Studios', '2024-05-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (108, 'Astroneer', 'Explore and reshape distant worlds in this sandbox adventure', 'Astroneer is System Era''s charming sandbox exploration game about colonizing alien planets in stylized solar system. As Astroneer during 25th century space gold rush, explore seven distinct planets with unique biomes, resources, hazards. Core loop revolves around gathering resources, researching technologies, building bases, terraforming using versatile Terrain Tool creating tunnels and structures. Seamless drop-in/drop-out co-op for up to four players. Discover modules like research chambers, printers, rovers, shuttles. Tether system provides oxygen while exploring. Each planet presents different challenges: wind storms, hostile flora, aggressive enemies, rare resources. Colorful whimsical art style makes experience relaxing. Vehicle customization, automation, cross-platform play, regular free updates. Chill yet satisfying sandbox perfect for exploration and building.', 29.99, 'https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQbJc96XUYGj48YjZZ-48_4bl-q7VxVCJtv8A&s', 'System Era', '2019-02-06', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (109, 'Marauders', 'Tactical first-person multiplayer looter shooter in space', 'Marauders is Small Impact Games'' dieselpunk multiplayer extraction shooter set in alternate 1990s where Earth industrialization forced humanity into space. Play space pirate raiding derelict freighters, abandoned stations, asteroid facilities for loot while competing against players and AI. Matches begin aboard small ship navigating space, choosing which station to raid. Ship-to-ship combat allows breaching and boarding. Once aboard, extraction loop begins: loot weapons, resources, materials while managing limited inventory and hostiles. Death means losing equipped gear, creating constant tension. Dieselpunk aesthetic features retrofuturistic 40s-50s design with spacefaring tech. Persistent progression unlocks new ships, weapons, gear. Emphasizes tactical gameplay with realistic weapons, no HUD, deadly time-to-kill. Proximity voice chat, airlock decompression dangers, player theft threat delivers intense high-risk gameplay.', 29.99, 'https://images8.alphacoders.com/127/thumb-1920-1276445.jpg', 'Small Impact Games', '2023-09-15', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (110, 'Hunt: Showdown', 'Competitive first-person bounty hunting game', 'Hunt: Showdown is Crytek''s unique PvPvE extraction shooter set in 1895 Louisiana. Play bounty hunters tracking nightmarish creatures while competing against players for same targets. Blend co-op monster hunting with competitive multiplayer—kill boss, banish it, collect bounty token, extract while other players converge using Dark Sight vision. Every sound matters: footsteps, crows scattering, disturbed horses, gunshots alert nearby hunters. Phenomenal audio design creates paranoia and tactical opportunities. Permanent death means losing hunter and loadout upon death. Hunters level up during matches gaining perks. Arsenal includes period-accurate weapons like lever-action rifles, revolvers, crossbows. Swamps populated with zombie Grunts, Hives, Immolators, boss monsters. Trios, duos, solo play. Unmatched tension and atmosphere in competitive multiplayer.', 39.99, 'https://i.redd.it/f4kf3vbh73d51.png', 'Crytek', '2019-08-27', 0);
INSERT INTO games (id, title, description, detailed_description, price, image_url, publisher, release_date, discount_percentage) VALUES (111, 'The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth', 'Roguelike dungeon crawler with thousands of items', 'The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth is Edmund McMillen''s roguelike masterpiece remake. Control Isaac escaping religiously deranged mother into nightmare basement filled with creatures inspired by biblical themes and body horror. Each run is procedurally generated with randomized rooms, items, enemies, bosses ensuring no two playthroughs are same. Over 600 items stack and combine in unexpected ways creating absurdly overpowered or terrible synergies. Unlock new characters with unique stats and abilities, new items, bosses, endings by completing challenges. Repentance expansion adds massive content update. Dozens of transformation possibilities, alternate paths, hidden secrets, brutally difficult optional challenges. "Just one more run" gameplay loop is irresistible. Dark humor, gross-out visuals, surprisingly emotional narrative hidden beneath biblical symbolism create unique experience that remains unmatched in depth.', 14.99, 'https://www.nintendo.com/eu/media/images/10_share_images/games_15/wiiu_download_software_5/SI_WiiUDS_TheBindingOfIsaacRebirth_image1600w.jpg', 'Nicalis', '2014-11-04', 0);
